var book = {
	"name": "2 Samuel",
	"numChapters": 24,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te hadien ka jingïap u Saul, haba u Dabid u la lah wan phai noh na kaba pynïap ïa ki Amalek, bad haba u Dabid u la shong ar sngi ha Siklag,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ha ka balai sngi te, ha khmih, u briew u la wan mih na ka jaka shong dara u Saul uba la kad ki jaiñ jong u, bad ka khyndew halor ka khlieh jong u; te haba u la wan poi ha u Dabid, u la hap ha khyndew, bad u la nguh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Dabid u la kylli ïa u, “Nangno me la wan?” U te u la ïathuh ha u, “Na ka dara ki Israel nga la phet ïap.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Dabid u la kylli ïa u, “Ka la long kumno? To ïathuh ha nga, nga kyrpad ïa me.” U ruh u la ïathuh, “U paidbah u la phet ïap na kata ka thma, bad shibun na uta u paidbah ki la kyllon bad ki la ïap: u Saul ruh bad u Jonathan u khun jong u ki la ïap noh.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Dabid u la kylli ïa uta u samla uba ïathuh ha u, “Kumno me tip ba ki la ïap u Saul bad u Jonathan u khun jong u?”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te uta u samla uba ïathuh ha u, u la ong, “Ka la jia ba nga don ha u lum Gilboa, te ha khmih, u Saul u la shaniah ha la u sum; ha khmih ruh, ki kali ïapom bad ki nongshong kulai ki ïabeh eh nadien jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba u la khmih shadien, u la ïohi ïa nga, bad u la khot ïa nga. Nga ruh nga la ong, ‘Nga hangne.’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u la kylli ïa nga, ‘Me uei?’ Te nga la ïathuh ha u, ‘Nga u nong Amalek.’",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u la ong pat ha nga, ‘Nga kyrpad ïa me, to ïeng hajan jong nga, bad pynïap ïa nga, naba ka jingpisa ka la ngat ha nga; namar ba ka jingim jong nga baroh ka dang sah ha nga.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta, nga la ïeng hajan jong u, bad nga la pynïap ïa u, naba nga la tip skhem ba um lah im shuh haba u la kyllon; bad nga la shim ïa kata ka pansngiat kaba ha ka khlieh jong u, bad ïa kata ka tad tyrpeng kaba ha ka ksang'ti jong u, bad nga la wallam ïa ki shane ha u kynrad jong nga.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la bat ïa la ki jaiñ, bad u la kad ïa ki; bad kumjuh uta paidbah baroh uba bad u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ki la sngewsih, bad ki la ïam, bad ki la shah jingit haduh janmiet, namar u Saul, bad namar u Jonathan u khun jong u, bad namar u paidbah jong U Trai, bad namar ka ïing Israel; namar ba ki la hap da ka waitlam.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha uta u samla uba la ïathuh ha u, “Me uba nangno?” U te u la ïathuh, “Nga u khun u nongwei, u nong Amalek.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Dabid te u la ong ha u, “Kumno ba mem shym la sheptieng ban rah ïa la ka kti ïa ka ban pynjot noh ïa uba la sleh jong U Trai?”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Dabid u la khot ïa uwei na kita ki samla, bad u la ong, “To leit hajan, to ktah kti ïa u.” U te u la shoh ïa u ba u la ïap noh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U Dabid te u la ong ha u, “To ka snam jong me kan long halor ka khlieh jong me; naba ka shyntur jong me hi ka la phla sakhi pyrshah ïa me, ka la ong, ‘Nga la pynïap ïa uba la sleh jong U Trai.’ ”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Dabid u la rwai da kane ka jingrwai sngewsynei namar u Saul bad namar u Jonathan u khun jong u:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> u la hukum ruh ban hikai ha ki khun Judah ïa ka jingrwai ka ryntieh: ha khmih, la thoh ïa ka ha Ka Kitab u Jasher:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Ïa ka burom jong me, ko Israel, la pynïap ha ki jaka bajrong jong me! kumno ki la kyllon kiba khlaiñ bor.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> To wat ïathuh ïa kane ha Gath, wat pynbna ha ki lynti shnong ka Ashkelon; ïoh kin kmen ki khun kynthei ki Philistia, ïoh kin kyrkoh ki khun kynthei jong kita ïa ki bym shym la otsher.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “A phi ki lum Gilboa, to wat ai kin long halor jong phi ka umjer lymne u slap, lymne ki lyngkha ki jingainguh: namar hangta la bred noh ïa ki stieh jong kiba khlaiñ bor, ka stieh u Saul, bym shym la pynsleh da ka umphniang.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Na ka snam jong kita ïa kiba la pynïap, na ka khleiñ jong kiba khlaiñ bor, ka ryntieh u Jonathan kam shym la phai dien, bad ka waitlam u Saul kam shym la phai noh suda.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “U Saul bad u Jonathan ki la long kiba ieit bad kiba sngewtynnad katba ki dang im, bad ha ka jingïap jong ki ym shym la pynkhlad ïa ki; ki la long kham stet ban ïa ki pukni, ki la kham khlaiñ ban ïa ki sing keiñ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Phi ki khun kynthei Israel, to ïam namar u Saul, uba pynkup ïa phi da ki jaiñ saw kiba kordor, uba pyndeng da ki jingdeng ksiar halor ki jaiñkup jong phi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Kumno ki la kyllon kiba khlaiñ bor hapdeng ka thma! “Ïa u Jonathan la pynïap ha ki jaka bajrong jong me.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Nga khuslai sat namar jong me, ko Jonathan, u para jong nga: nga la sngewtynnad eh ïa me: ka jingieit jong me ïa nga ka la long kaba phylla, kaba palat ïa ka jingieit ki kynthei keiñ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Kumno ki la kyllon kiba khlaiñ bor, bad ba la jot noh kita ki atiar ïapom!”"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hadien kane te, u Dabid u la kylli na U Trai, u da ong, “Ngan leit kiew ne em sha kano kano na ki nongbah Judah?” Bad U Trai u la ïathuh ha u, “To leit kiew.” Te u Dabid u la kylli, “Shano ngan leit kiew?” U te U la ïathuh, “Sha Hebron.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kumta, u Dabid u la leit kiew shatei, lem bad ki ar ngut ki tnga jong u ruh, ka Ahinoam ka nong Jesril, bad ka Abigail ka nong Karmel, ka tnga u Nabal.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ïalam artet ïa la ki rangbah ruh kiba don lem bad u, uwei uwei ruh bad la kiba ha ïing; te ki la shong ha ki shnong Hebron.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ki Judah ki la ïawan, bad ki la pynsleh hangta ïa u Dabid ban long syiem halor ka ïing Judah. Te ki la ïathuh ha u Dabid, ki ïa-ong, “Dei ki Jabesh-gilead kiba la tep ïa u Saul.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Dabid u la phah ki nongkit-ktien sha ki Jabesh-gilead, bad u la ong ha ki, “To long phi ïa kiba la kyrkhu na U Trai, kiba la leh ïa kane ka jingleh isynei ha u kynrad jong phi, u Saul keiñ, bad ba phi la tep ïa u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> To U Trai te un leh isynei bad ka jingshisha ruh ïa phi: bad ma nga ruh ngan ai nong ïa phi namar kane ka jinglehbha, namar ba phi la leh ïa kane ka jingleh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Namar kata te, to pynkhlaiñ ïa la ki kti, bad to long shlur phi: namar u kynrad jong phi u Saul u la ïap noh, ka ïing Judah ruh ki la pynsleh ïa nga ban long syiem halor jong ki.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, u Abner u khun u Ner, u kaptan u paidïapom u Saul, u la lah shim ïa u Ishbosheth u khun u Saul, bad u la ïalam ïa u sha shiliang sha Mahanaim;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad u la pynlong syiem ïa u halor ka Gilead, bad halor ki Ashur, bad halor ka Jesril, bad halor ki Ephraim, bad halor ki Benjamin, bad halor ki Israel baroh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> (U Ishbosheth u khun u Saul u la sawphew snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Israel, bad u la synshar ar snem.) Te ka ïing Judah ki la bud ïa u Dabid.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ka por ba u Dabid u la long syiem ha Hebron halor ka ïing Judah ka la long hynñiew snem bad hynriew bnai.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Abner u khun u Ner, bad ki shakri u Ishbosheth u khun u Saul, ki la ïamih noh na Mahanaim sha Gibeon.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u Joab u khun ka Seruïah, bad ki shakri u Dabid, ki la ïamih noh, bad ki la ïashem ïa ki hajan ka pung Gibeon; bad ki la ïashong, kine sha kane ka liang ka pung, bad kita sha kawei pat ka liang ka pung.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Abner u la ong ha u Joab, “To kine ki samla kin ïaïeng mynta, bad kin ïalehkai ha khmat jong ngi.” Bad u Joab u la ong, “To kin ïaïeng.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te kumta ki la ïaïeng bad ki la leit shiliang ha la ka jingkheiñ; khat-ar ngut na ka bynta ki Benjamin, kata, na ka bynta u Ishbosheth u khun u Saul, bad khat-ar ngut ki shakri u Dabid.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad uwei uwei baroh u la kem ïa la u briew na ka khlieh, bad u la dung ïa la ka waitlam na krung u briew jong u; kumta, ki la ïakyllon ryngkat: namar kata, la khot ïa kata ka jaka “Helkath-hassurim”, kaba ha Gibeon.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ka thma ka la jur eh ha kata ka sngi; bad la jop ïa u Abner, bad ïa u paidïapom ki Israel, ha khmat ki shakri u Dabid.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ki khun ka Seruïah lai ngut ki la don hangta, u Joab, bad u Abishai, bad u Asahel: te u Asahel u la long uba stet ki kjat jong u kat ka skei kaba ha khlaw.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u Asahel u la beh nadien u Abner; bad ha kaba leit um shym phai sha kamon lymne sha kadiang na kaba beh ïa u Abner.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Abner u la kyrtiang dien, bad u la kylli, “Ma me u Asahel?” U ruh u la ïathuh, “Ma nga keiñ.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u Abner u la ong ha u, “To phai sha kamon lane sha kadiang, bad to kem ha me ïa uwei na kita ki samla, bad shim ïa ki atiar ïapom jong u.” Hynrei, u Asahel um treh ban phai noh na kaba beh ïa u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Abner u la ong pat ha u Asahel, “To phai noh na kaba beh nadien jong nga: ngan shoh pynkyllon ïa me balei? naba kumno ngan da khmied la ka khmat ha u Joab u hynmen jong me hadien?”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> La kumta ruh um treh ban phai noh: namar kata, u Abner u la sum ïa u da ka tdong u sum na ka kpoh, bad uta u sum u la mih noh na shadien jong u; te u la kyllon hangta, bad u la ïap ha kata hi ka jaka: bad baroh kat kiba wan poi ha kata ka jaka ha kaba u Asahel u la kyllon bad ba u la ïap ki la ïasangeh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hynrei, u Joab bad u Abishai ki la ïabeh nadien u Abner; te hamar ba la sep ka sngi ki la poi sha u lum Ammah, uba ha marpyrshah ka Giah ha ka lynti ka ri khlaw Gibeon.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ki khun u Benjamin ki la ïalum lang hadien u Abner, bad ki la ïawan long uwei u paidbah, bad ki la ïeng halor uwei u lum.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ynda kumta, u Abner u la pyrta ha u Joab, bad u la ong, “Ka waitlam kan pynjot noh junom? balei mem tip ba ha ka bakut kan long ka jingkthang? haba kumta te, men slem pat sa katno, ïa ka ban hukum ïa u paidbah ba kin phai noh na kaba beh ïa la ki para?”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te u Joab u la ong, “Katba im U Blei, lada mem shym la kren ma me, shisha la mynhynne mynstep u paidbah u la lah leit wan noh na kaba beh uwei uwei ïa la u para.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta, u Joab u la put ïa ka ronsing, bad u paidbah baroh u la sangeh noh, bad kim shym la beh shuh ïa ki Israel, bad kim shym la ïaleh thma shuh.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u Abner bad ki rangbah jong u ki la ïaid baroh shi miet halor ka madan: bad ki la leit sha shiliang ka Jordan, bad ki la leit lyngba ïa ka Bithron baroh, bad ki la wan poi ha Mahanaim.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u Joab u la leit wan noh na kaba beh ïa u Abner: te haba u la lum lang ïa u paidbah baroh, ki la duna na ki shakri u Dabid khatkhyndai ngut ki rangbah bad u Asahel ruh.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hynrei, ki shakri u Dabid ki la shoh pynïap na ki Benjamin, bad na ki rangbah u Abner, laispah hynriewphew ngut ki briew.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te ki la shim ïa u Asahel, bad ki la tep ïa u ha ka jingtep u kpa jong u, kaba ha Bethlehem. Bad u Joab bad u paidbah jong u ki la ïaid baroh shi miet, bad ki la poi sha Hebron hamar kaba mih ka sngi."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ka thma kaba slem ka la don hapdeng ka ïing u Saul bad ka ïing u Dabid: hynrei, u Dabid u la nang khlaiñ nang khlaiñ, bad ka ïing u Saul ka la nang kham tlot kham tlot.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te la kha ki khun shynrang ïa u Dabid ha Hebron: bad uba la kha nyngkong jong u, u la long u Amnon, na ka Ahinoam ka nong Jesril;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad u ba-ar jong u, u Khileab, na ka Abigail ka tnga u Nabal u nong Karmel; bad u balai, u Absalom, u khun ka Maakah kaba ka khun u Talmai u syiem ka Gesur;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad u basaw, u Adonijah, u khun ka Haggith; bad u basan, u Shephatiah u khun ka Abital;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad u bahynriew, u Ithream, na ka Eglah ka tnga u Dabid. Ïa kine keiñ la kha ïa u Dabid ha Hebron.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te mynba ka la don ka thma hapdeng ka ïing u Saul bad ka ïing u Dabid, u Abner u la ïaleh tyngeh na ka bynta ka ïing u Saul.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, u Saul u la don ka tnga kliar, kaba kyrteng “ka Rispah”, ka khun u Aïah: bad u Ishbosheth u la ong ha u Abner, “Balei ba me la rung sha ka tnga kliar u kpa jong nga?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda kumta, u Abner u la khih bitar lep namar kita ki ktien u Ishbosheth, bad u la ong, “Nga, nga long tang ka khlieh ksew uba dei ïa ka Judah mo? Ha kane ka sngi nga leh isynei ïa ka ïing u Saul u kpa jong me, bad ïa ki para jong u, bad ïa ki lok jong u, bad ngam shym la ai noh ïa me ha ka kti u Dabid, pynban, me tei pop halor nga ha kane ka sngi namar kane ka briew?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> To U Blei un leh kumta ïa u Abner, bad un pyntam ruh, lada, kumba U Trai u la smai ha u Dabid, nga ngam leh kumta ïa u;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> da kaba pynphai noh ïa ka jinglong syiem na ka ïing u Saul, bad pynïeng la ka khet u Dabid halor ki Israel bad halor ki Judah, naduh Dan haduh Beer-sheba.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U ruh um shym nud shuh ban ïathuh shikyntien ïa u Abner, namar ba u la sheptieng ïa u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Abner u la phah ki nongkit-ktien ha u Dabid na ka bynta ïa lade, u da ong, “Kane ka ri ka jongno?” u ong ruh, “To pynlong jutang bad nga, te ha khmih, ka kti jong nga kan long lem bad me, ïa ka ban pynwan sha me ïa ki Israel baroh.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U ruh u la ong, “Ñiuma; ngan pynlong jutang bad me: hynrei, ïa kane kawei nga dawa na me, kata ka long, men ym ïohi ïa ka khmat jong nga, lymda me wallam shuwa ïa ka Mikhal ka khun u Saul, haba me wan ïohi ïa ka khmat jong nga.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Dabid u la phah ïa ki nongkit-ktien ha u Ishbosheth u khun u Saul, u da ong, “Ai noh ha nga ïa ka tnga jong nga, ka Mikhal keiñ, ïa kaba nga la tehktien na ka bynta shispah tylli ki sher jong ki Philistia.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Ishbosheth u la phah, bad u la shim noh ïa ka na u tnga jong ka, na u Phaltiel u khun u Laish keiñ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad uta u tnga jong ka u la leit on ïa ka, u da leit u da ïam ruh hadien jong ka haduh Bahurim. Hangta u Abner u la ong ha u, “Khie leit wan noh:” u ruh u la leit wan noh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Abner u la ïakren bad ki tymmen basan ki Israel, u da ong, “Mynhynnin mynshisngi phi la wad ïa u Dabid ban long syiem halor jong phi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Mynta te, to leh kumta: naba U Trai u la kren shaphang u Dabid, u da ong, ‘Da ka kti u Dabid u shakri jong nga ngan pyllait ïa ki briew jong nga ki Israel na ka kti ki Philistia, bad na ka kti ki nongshun jong ki baroh.’ ”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u Abner u la ïakren bad ki Benjamin ruh de: bad u Abner u la leit ïa ka ban ïakren ruh bad u Dabid ha Hebron shaphang kita kiei kiei kiba ibit ha ki Israel, bad ha ka ïing ki Benjamin baroh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kumta, u Abner u la wan poi sha u Dabid ha Hebron, bad arphew ngut ki rangbah ryngkat bad u. Bad u Dabid u la thaw ka jingkhawai ïa u Abner bad ïa kita ki rangbah kiba bad u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u Abner u la ong ha u Dabid, “Ngan khie bad ngan leit, bad ngan lum ïa ki Israel baroh ha u syiem kynrad jong nga, ba kin ïohthaw jutang bad me, bad ba men ïoh synshar halor baroh katba kwah ka dohnud jong me.” Bad u Dabid u la phah noh ïa u Abner; u ruh u la leit da kaba suk.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ha khmih, ki shakri u Dabid bad u Joab ki la wan na kaba beh ïa uwei u paid, bad ki la wallam lem bad ki ka jinglute kaba khraw: hynrei, u Abner um shym don bad u Dabid ha Hebron; naba u la lah phah noh ïa u, u ruh u la lah leit da kaba suk.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Haba u Joab te bad uta u paidïapom baroh uba bad u ki la ïawan, la ïathuh ha u Joab, da kaba ong, “U Abner u khun u Ner u la wan sha u syiem, u ruh u la phah noh ïa u, bad u la leit da kaba suk.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te u Joab u la leit sha u syiem, bad u la ong, “Me la leh aïu? ha khmih, u Abner u la wan sha me; balei te me la phah noh ïa u, bad ba u la leit noh?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Me ithuh ïa u Abner u khun u Ner, ba u la wan khnang ban shukor ïa me, ban tip ïa ka jingmih shabar jong me bad ïa ka jingwan shapoh jong me bad ba un tip ïa kiei kiei baroh ïa kiba me leh.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te haba u Joab u la mih noh na u Dabid, u la phah ki nongkit-ktien hadien u Abner, bad ki la wallam noh pat ïa u na ka pukri u Sirah: hynrei, u Dabid um shym tip ïa kata.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te haba u Abner u la wan phai noh sha Hebron, u Joab u la shim kyrpang ïa u shapdeng ka khyrdop ban ïakren bad u da kaba suk, bad u la shoh ïa u hangta na ka kpoh, ba kumta u la ïap noh, namar ka snam u Asahel u para jong u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Hadien kata, te u Dabid u la ïohsngew, bad u la ong, “Ma nga bad ka hima jong nga ngi khuid keiñ ha khmat U Trai junom na ka snam u Abner u khun u Ner:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> to kan hap keiñ ha ka khlieh u Joab, bad ha ka ïing u kpa jong u baroh: bad wat ai ban duh na ka ïing u Joab u bapang liat ksuit, lane u bapang 'thohlieh, lane uba shan ha u diengduh, lane uba hap da ka waitlam; lane u bakyrduh kpu.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kumta, u Joab bad u Abishai u para jong u ki la pynïap ïa u Abner, namar ba u ruh u la pynïap ïa u Asahel u para jong ki ha ka thma ha Gibeon.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong ha u Joab, bad ha uta u paidbah baroh uba don lem bad u, “To kad ïa la ki jaiñ, bad to panpoh ïa lade ha ka jaiñ khain, bad to ïambriew ha khmat u Abner.” Bad u Dabid syiem ruh u la bud hadien ka krong.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad ki la tep ïa u Abner ha Hebron: bad u syiem u la pynjam ïa la ka ktien, bad u la ïam ha ka jingtep u Abner; bad u paidbah baroh ruh u la ïam.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u syiem u la rwai sngewsynei namar u Abner, bad u la ong, “U Abner u dei ban ïap kumba u ïap uba bieit?",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ïa ki kti jong me ym shym la khum, lymne ym shym la buh ïa ki kjat jong me ha ki narkjat; kumba kyllon u briew ha khmat ki khun ka pop, kumta me la kyllon.” Bad u paidbah baroh ki la nang ïam shuh shuh namar jong u.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te u paidbah baroh ki la ïawan katba ka dang shai ïa ka ban pynbam kpu ïa u Dabid; hynrei, u Dabid u la smai, u da ong, “Kumne U Blei un leh ïa nga, bad tam ruh, lada ngan mad ïa u kpu, lymne ïa kaei kaei ruh, tad ynda la sep ka sngi.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad u paidbah baroh ki la khmih ïa kata, bad ka la pynsngewbha ïa ki: bad kiei kiei baroh kiba u la leh u syiem ka la pynsngewbha ïa u paidbah baroh.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad u paidbah baroh ki la sngewthuh ha kata ka sngi ba ym shym long na u syiem ba la pynïap ïa u Abner u khun u Ner.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad u syiem u la ong ha la ki shakri, “Balei, phim tip ba u nongïalam bad u rangbah u bakhraw batri u la kyllon ha Israel ha kane ka sngi?",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Ma nga te la la thung syiem ruh ïa nga, nga long uba tlot ha kane ka sngi; bad kine ki rangbah, ki khun ka Seruïah ki kham eh ïa nga: to U Trai un ai nong ïa u nongleh sniew katba kum ka jingbymman jong u.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba u khun u Saul u la ïohsngew ba u la ïap u Abner ha Hebron, ki kti jong u ki la duh bor, bad ki Israel baroh ki la khuslai.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u khun u Saul u la don ar ngut ki rangbah kiba la long ki kaptan ïa ka kynhun: ka kyrteng uwei “u Baanah”, bad ka kyrteng uta uwei “u Rekhab”, ki khun u Rimmon u nong Beeroth, na ki khun u Benjamin: (naba ïa ka Beeroth ruh la ñiew ka jong ki Benjamin:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> te ki Beeroth ki la phet ïap sha Gittaim, bad hangta ki la sah kum ki sohshnong haduh kane ka sngi.)",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Jonathan, u khun u Saul, u la don u khun u ba-dkoh ki kjat. Une, u la san snem ka rta haba la poi ka jingbna na Jesril shaphang u Saul bad u Jonathan, te ka nongsumar ka la shim, ka la rah ïa u bad ka la phet ïap: ka la jia te katba ka la pynkloi ban phet, ba u la hap, bad u la dkoh. Bad ka kyrteng jong u ka la long “u Mephibosheth”.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te kine ki khun u Rimmon u nong Beeroth, u Rekhab bad u Baanah, ki la leit, bad ki la poi sha ka ïing u Ishbosheth hamar kaba la shit ka sngi, haba u dang thiah kai ha kaba shiteng sngi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki la leit bsut shapoh ïing, kum ban sa wan shim Kew; bad ki la shoh ïa u na ka kpoh: bad u Rekhab bad u Baanah u para jong u ki la ïaphet ïap noh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Naba u dang thiah ha la ka jingthiah ha ka kamra thiah jong u, haba ki la rung shapoh ïing, bad ki la shoh pynïap ïa u, bad ki la khrai ïa ka khlieh jong u, bad ki la shim ïa kata ka khlieh, bad ki la ïaid ïa kata ka madan baroh shi miet.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki la wallam ïa ka khlieh u Ishbosheth sha u Dabid ha Hebron, bad ki la ong ha u syiem, “Ha khmih ïa ka khlieh u Ishbosheth u khun u Saul u nongshun jong me, uba la wad ïa ka jingim jong me; te ha kane ka sngi U Trai u la pynhiar ïa ka kput u syiem kynrad jong nga halor u Saul, bad halor u symbai jong u.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U Dabid te u la ïathuh ha u Rekhab bad u Baanah u para jong u, ki khun u Rimmon u nong Beeroth, bad u la ong ha ki, “Katba im U Trai, uba la pyllait ïa ka mynsiem jong nga na ka jingjynjar baroh,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> haba u la ïathuh uwei ha nga, u da ong, ‘Ha khmih, u Saul u la ïap noh,’ u da tharai ba u la wallam ka khubor ka babha, nga la kem ïa u, bad nga la pynïap ïa u ha Siklag, kata keiñ ka la long ka bainong ba nga la ai ïa u, namar kata ka khubor jong u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Katno tam te, haba ki briew bymman ki la pynïap ïa u briew u bahok ha la ïing halor ka jingthiah jong u, ngan ym dawa ïa ka snam jong u na ki kti jong phi, bad pynduh noh ïa phi na ka khyndew?”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Dabid u la hukum ïa ki samla jong u, ki ruh ki la pynïap ïa ki, bad ki la ot noh ïa ki kti jong ki bad ïa ki kjat jong ki, bad ki la sdien ïa ki hajan ka pung kaba ha Hebron. Hynrei, ïa ka khlieh u Ishbosheth ki la shim, bad ki la tep ha ka jingtep u Abner ha Hebron."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, ki jaid Israel baroh ki la ïawan ha u Dabid sha Hebron, bad ki la kren, ki ïa-ong, “Ha khmih, ngi long ka shyieng jong me bad ka doh jong me.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Mynshuwa ruh, mynba u Saul u la long syiem halor jong ngi, long ma me uba la ju ïalam shabar bad uba wallam shapoh ïa ki Israel: bad U Trai u la ong ha me, ‘Men bsa ma me ïa ki briew jong nga ki Israel, bad men long u nongïalam ïa ki Israel.’ ”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kumta, ki tymmen basan ki Israel baroh ki la ïawan ha u syiem sha Hebron; bad u syiem Dabid u la teh jutang bad ki ha Hebron ha khmat U Trai: bad ki la pynsleh ïa u Dabid ban long syiem halor ki Israel.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Dabid u la laiphew snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar, bad u la synshar sawphew snem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ha Hebron u la synshar hynñiew snem hynriew bnai halor ki Judah: bad ha Jerusalem u la synshar laiphew lai snem halor ki Israel bad ki Judah baroh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u syiem bad u paid jong u ki la leit sha Jerusalem ban ïaleh ïa ki Jebus, kiba ki trai-shnong jong kata ka ri: kiba la kren ha u Dabid, ki ïa-ong, “Men ym ïoh wan shane, lymda men shim noh ïa ki bamatlah bad ïa ki ba-dkoh:” ki da mut, “U Dabid um lah rung shane.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Pynban, u Dabid u la jop ïa ka kut jong ka Seïon; kata ka long “Ka nongbah u Dabid”.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ha kata ka sngi, u Dabid u la ong, “Jar u ban pom ïa ki Jebus, to un leit kiew na kane ka nur um, bad un pom ïa kita ki ba-dkoh bad ïa ki bamatlah, kiba ka mynsiem u Dabid ka isih.” Namar kata, ki ïa-ong, “Ki bamatlah bad ki ba-dkoh ki hangta; um lah rung ruh shapoh ïing.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Dabid u la shong ha kata ka kut, bad u la khot kyrteng ïa ka “Ka nongbah u Dabid”. Bad u Dabid u la tei kynroh baroh sawdong naduh Millo bad shapoh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Dabid u la nang ïoh bor nang ïoh bor; bad U Trai, U Blei ki paid, u la don ryngkat bad u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Hiram u syiem ka Tyros u la phah ki nongkit-ktien ha u Dabid, bad ki dieng Kedar, bad ïa ki misteri dieng, bad ki misteri maw: bad ki la tei ïing ïa u Dabid.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Dabid u la tip ba U Trai u la pynskhem ïa u ban long syiem halor ki Israel, bad ba U la pynkyntiew ïa ka jinglong syiem jong u na ka bynta ki briew jong U, ki Israel keiñ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Dabid u la shim shuh shuh ïa ki tnga kliar bad ki tnga trai na Jerusalem, hadien ba u la wan noh na Hebron: bad la nang kha ha u Dabid ki khun shynrang bad kynthei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad kine ki kyrteng jong kita kiba la kha ha u ha Jerusalem; u Shammua, bad u Shobab, bad u Nathan, bad u Solomon,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> u Ibhar ruh, bad u Elishua; bad u Nepheg, bad u Japhia;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad u Elishama, bad u Eliada, bad u Eliphelet.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te haba ki Philistia ki la ïohsngew ba ki la lah pynsleh ïa u Dabid ban long syiem halor ki Israel, ki Philistia baroh ki la wan kiew ban wad ïa u Dabid; bad u Dabid u la ïohsngew, bad u la leit hiar sha kata ka kut.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ki Philistia ki la wan bad ki la saphred ïa lade ha ka them Rephaim.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u Dabid u la kylli na U Trai, u da ong, “Ngan leit kiew ne em ban ïaleh ïa ki Philistia? Men ai noh ne em ïa ki ha ka kti jong nga?” Bad U Trai u la ïathuh ha u Dabid, “Khie leit kiew; naba ngan ai noh shisha ïa kine ki Philistia ha ka kti jong me.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Dabid u la leit sha Baal-perasim, bad u Dabid u la shoh pynïap ïa ki hangta; bad u la ong, “U Trai u la pynsaphred ïa ki nongshun jong nga ha shuwa jong nga, kumba pynsaphred ïa ka um.” Namar kata, u la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “Baal-perasim”.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ki la iehnoh noh hangta ïa ki durblei jong ki, bad u Dabid bad u paidbah jong u ki la shim noh ïa ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ki Philistia ki la wan kiew pat sa shi sien, bad ki la saphred ïa lade ha ka them Rephaim.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba u Dabid u la kylli na U Trai, U la ong ha u, “Wat leit kiew: hynrei, leit sawdong na shadien jong ki, bad kyntur sha ki ha marpyrshah kita ki dieng Bekaim.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te haba me ïohsngew ka jingsawa kum ka jingïaid ha ki kliar jong kita ki dieng Bekaim, hangta te men pynkhih ïa lade: namar haba kumta, U Trai un leit mih ha shuwa jong me ïa ka ban shoh pynïap ïa u paid jong ki Philistia.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Dabid u la leh kumta, kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u; bad u la shoh pynïap ïa ki Philistia naduh Geba haduh kaba poi sha Geser."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Dabid u la lum lang pat ïa kiba la kynsai jong ki Israel baroh, jin laiphew hajar ngut.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ïeng bad u la leit lem bad uta u paidbah baroh uba bad u, na Baale Judah ïa ka ban wallam artet ïa ka synduk U Blei, ïa kaba la khot da kata ka Kyrteng, ka kyrteng U Trai ki paid keiñ uba shong hapdeng ki Kherub.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki la buh ïa kata ka synduk U Blei ha ka kali ka bathymmai, bad ki la wallam ïa ka na ka ïing u Abinadab, kaba ha Gibeah: te u Ussah bad u Ahio, ki khun u Abinadab, ki la ñiah ïa kata ka kali ka bathymmai.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ki la wallam ïa ka na ka ïing u Abinadab, kaba ha Gibeah, lem bad kata ka synduk U Blei: bad u Ahio u la ïaid ha shuwa kata ka synduk.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Dabid bad ka ïing Israel baroh ki la tem ha khmat U Trai ïa ki jingtem baroh kiba da u dieng Kseh, ïa ki duitara, ïa ki nebel, ïa ki kanjari, ïa ki manirai, bad ïa ki shakuriaw de.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba ki la poi sha ka kyntem u Nakon, u Ussah u la rah ïa la ka kti sha kata ka synduk U Blei, bad u la bat ïa ka; naba kita ki masi ki la jynthut.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ka jingbitar U Trai ka la meh lep ïa u Ussah; bad U Blei u la shoh ïa u hangta namar kata ka jingleh klet; bad hangta u la ïap hajan kata ka synduk U Blei.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Dabid u la sngewsih namar ba U Trai u la tur pynïap ïa u Ussah: bad u la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “ka Peres-Ussah”, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Dabid u la sheptieng ïa U Trai ha kata ka sngi; bad u la ong, “Kumno kan wan ka synduk U Trai sha nga?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta, u Dabid um treh shuh ban pynkynriah ïa ka synduk U Trai ha lade sha ka nongbah u Dabid; hynrei, u Dabid u la pynphai ïa ka sha ïing u Obed-edom u nong Gath.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ka synduk U Trai ka la sah ha ïing u Obed-edom u nong Gath lai bnai: te U Trai u la kyrkhu ïa u Obed-edom, bad ïa ka ïing jong u baroh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te la ïathuh ha u syiem Dabid, da kaba ong, “U Trai u la kyrkhu ïa ka ïing u Obed-edom, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh ki jong u, na ka bynta kata ka synduk U Blei.” Kumta te, u Dabid u la leit wallam noh artet ïa ka synduk U Blei na ïing u Obed-edom sha ka nongbah u Dabid da ka jingkmen.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te haba kita kiba bah ïa ka synduk U Trai ki la nang leit hynriew sien-jam, hangta u la kñia ïa u masi dab bad ïa kiba sngaid.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Dabid u la shad katba u lah ha khmat U Trai; bad u Dabid u la phong da ka ephod linen.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kumta, u Dabid bad ka ïing Israel baroh ki la wallam noh artet ïa ka synduk U Trai da ka jingrisa, bad ka jingsawa ka ronsing.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te katba ka synduk U Trai ka la wan poi shapoh ka nongbah u Dabid, hangta ka Mikhal ka khun u Saul haba ka la khmih na ka jingkhang ïit, ka la ïohi ïa u syiem Dabid ba u da rynsied bad ba u da shad ha khmat U Trai; bad ka la beiñ ïa u ha la ka dohnud.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ki la wallam shapoh ïa kata ka synduk U Trai, bad ki la buh ïa ka ha la ka jaka, hapdeng kata Ka Tabernakl ïa kaba u Dabid u la pynïeng na ka bynta jong ka: bad u Dabid u la kñia ainguh da ki jingainguh thang bad ki jingainguh bapynïasuk ha khmat U Trai.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ynda u Dabid u la pyndep ban kñia ainguh ïa kita ki jingainguh thang bad ïa kita ki jingainguh bapynïasuk, u la kyrkhu keiñ ïa uta u paidbah ha ka kyrteng U Trai ki paid.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u la sam ha kita ki briew baroh, kata ha u paidlang ki Israel baroh, ha ki shynrang bad ha ki kynthei ruh, ha uwei pa uwei baroh, uwei u kpu, bad shi tukra ka doh, bad iwei i kpu da u soh Khajur. Kumta uta u paidbah baroh ki la leit wan noh uwei pa uwei baroh ha la ka jong ka ïing.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la leit phai noh ïa ka ban kyrkhu ïa la ki ba-ha-ïing. Te ka Mikhal ka khun u Saul ka la leit tan ïa u Dabid, bad ka la ong, “A katno uba donburom mo u syiem ki Israel u la long ha kane ka sngi, uba ha kane ka sngi u la pynlyngkhuit ïa lade ha khmat ki shakri kynthei jong ki shakri jong u, kumjuh kumba u 'riewthala u pynlyngkhuit khlem rain ïa lade!”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha ka Mikhal, “Ka la long ha khmat U Trai keiñ, uba la jied ïa nga pynban, ban ïa u kpa jong pha, bad ban ïa ka ïing jong u baroh, u da thung ïa nga ban long u nongïalam halor u paidbah jong U Trai, halor ki Israel: namar kata, ngan nang leh sngewbha ruh ha khmat U Trai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ngan long uba kham ibeiñ pat ban ïa kane, bad ngan long uba ibeiñ ha la ka jong ka jingñiew: hynrei, kita ki shakri kynthei ba pha la kren shaphang jong ki, kita keiñ kin pyndonburom ïa nga.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ka Mikhal ka khun u Saul kam shym la ïoh khun haduh ka sngi ka jingïap jong ka."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Haba u syiem te u la shong ha la ïing, bad ba U Trai u la ai kaba jahthait ïa u na ki nongshun jong u baroh kylleng sawdong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> u syiem u la ong ha u Nathan u nongïathuhlypa, “Ha khmih mynta, nga, nga shong ha ka ïing dieng Kedar, hynrei, ka synduk U Blei ka shong hapoh ki jaiñ.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Nathan u la ong ha u syiem, “Khie, to leh ïa kiei kiei baroh kiba ha ka dohnud jong me; naba U Trai u don lem bad me.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ha kata ka miet, ka la jia ba ka ktien U Trai ka la wan ha u Nathan, ka da ong,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Khie leit ïathuh ïa u shakri jong nga u Dabid, ‘Kumne u ong U Trai: Men tei ma me mo ïa ka ïing ha nga ba ngan shong ha ka?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Namar ngam shym shong ha ka ïing naduh kata ka sngi ba nga la wallam artet ïa ki khun Israel na ka ri Ijipt, haduh kane ka sngi, hynrei, nga la ïaid ha ka ïingjaiñ bad ïa Ka Tabernakl.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ha kita ki jaka baroh ha kiba nga la ïaid ryngkat bad ki khun Israel baroh, nga la kren shikyntien ne em ha kano kano ruh na ki jaid ki Israel, ïa kiba nga la hukum ba kin bsa ïa ki briew jong nga ki Israel, da kaba ong, “Balei ba phim shym la tei ka ïing dieng Kedar ïa nga?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Mynta te men ong kumne ïa u Dabid u shakri jong nga, “Kumne u ong U Trai ki paid: Nga la shim ïa me na kata ka jingker, bad na kaba bud ïa ki langbrot, ïa ka ban long u nongïalam halor ki briew jong nga, halor ki Israel keiñ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad nga la don ryngkat bad me kat shaba me la leit, bad nga la ot noh ïa ki nongshun jong me baroh na khmat jong me; bad ngan pynlong ïa me ka nam ka bakhraw, kum ka nam jong ki bakhraw tam kiba ha ka pyrthei.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ngan buh jaka ruh ïa ki briew jong nga ki Israel, bad ngan thung ïa ki, ba kin ïoh shong ha la ka jong ka jaka, bad ba kin ym kynriah noh shuh; te ki khun ka pop kin ym ïoh pynjynjar shuh ïa ki, kumba mynshuwa,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad kumba ka la long naduh kata ka sngi ba nga la thung ïa ki nongbishar halor ki briew jong nga ki Israel keiñ: bad ngan ai kaba jahthait ïa me na ki nongshun jong me baroh.” U Trai u pyntip ruh ïa me ba U Trai un pynlong ka ïing ïa me.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Haba la pynkut noh ïa ki sngi jong me, bad ba me la ïohthiah noh bad ki kpa jong me, ngan pynïeng ïa u symbai jong me hadien jong me, u ban mih noh na ka kpoh jong me, bad ngan pynskhem ïa ka jinglong syiem jong u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Un tei ma u keiñ ïa ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng jong nga; nga ruh ngan pynskhem ïa ka khet ka jinglong syiem jong u junom.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ma nga ngan dei khun ïa u, u ruh un dei kpa ïa nga: lada un leh palat, ngan sneng sympat ïa u da u dieng sympat briew, bad da ki jingshoh khun bynriew;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> hynrei, ka jingisynei jong nga kan ym kynriah noh na u, kumba nga la shim noh na u Saul, ïa uba nga la kyntait noh ha khmat jong me.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ïa ka ïing jong me bad ïa ka jinglong syiem jong me yn pynskhem ha khmat jong me junom: yn pynskhem keiñ ïa ka khet jong me junom.’ ”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Katba kum kine ki ktien baroh, bad katba kum kane ka jingithuhpaw baroh, kumta keiñ u Nathan u la kren ha u Dabid.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem Dabid u la leit bsut, bad u la shong ha khmat U Trai; bad u la ong, “Nga, nga long uei, A Trai U Blei, bad ka ïing jong nga ka long aïu, ba me la wallam ïa nga haduh hangne?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad kane ka la long pynban ka barit ha khmat jong me, A Trai U Blei; hynrei, me la kren shaphang ka ïing u shakri jong me sha ka ban slem eh ruh; bad kane ruh kat kum ka rukom briew, A Trai U Blei!",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Dabid un lah ong aïu pat ïa me? naba ma me, A Trai U Blei, me ithuh ïa la u shakri.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ka bynta ka ktien jong me hi, bad katba kum ka dohnud jong me hi, me la leh ïa kane kaba khraw baroh, ïa ka ban pyntip ïa ka ha la u shakri.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Namar kata, me long u bakhraw, A Trai U Blei; naba ym don uba kat ma me, lymne ym don U Blei nalor jong me, katba kum kata baroh ïa kaba ngi la ïohsngew da la ki shkor.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad kano ka jaid bynriew kawei ha ka khyndew kaba kum u paidlang jong me, kum ki Israel keiñ, ïa kaba U Blei u la leit ban pynim, ba kin long u paidlang ïa u hi, bad ban pynlong ïa lade ka nam, bad ban leh na ka bynta jong phi ïa kiei kiei ki bakhraw, bad ïa kiei kiei kiba itriem na ka bynta ka ri jong me, ha khmat u paidlang jong me, kiba me la pynim na ka ri Ijipt na ka bynta ïa lade, na kita ki jaid bynriew bad na ki blei jong ki?",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Namar me la pynskhem ha lade ïa u paidlang jong me, ïa ki Israel keiñ, ba kin long u paidlang ïa me hi junom; naba ma me, A Trai, me la jia long U Blei jong ki.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Mynta te, A Trai U Blei, to pynskhem junom ïa kata ka ktien kaba me la kren shaphang u shakri jong me, bad shaphang kata ka ïing jong u, bad to leh ruh kumba me la ong.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad to ai ba ka kyrteng jong me kan long ïa kaba la pynkhraw junom, da kaba ong, ‘U Trai ki paid u long U Blei halor ki Israel:’ bad to ai ba ka ïing u Dabid u shakri jong me kan long ïa kaba la pynskhem ha khmat jong me.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Namar ma me, A Trai ki paid, U Blei ki Israel, me la pynbna ha la u shakri, da kaba ong, ‘Ngan tei ïa me ka ïing’: namar kata keiñ, u shakri jong me u la shem ha la ka dohnud ïa ka ban duwai ha me ïa kane ka jingduwai.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te mynta, A Trai U Blei, me, me long U Blei, bad ki ktien jong me ki long ka jingshisha, bad me la kular ïa la u shakri ïa kane ka jingbha:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> namar kata, to men sngewbha ban kyrkhu ïa ka ïing u shakri jong me, ba kan ïaisah ha khmat jong me junom: naba me la kren ma me ïa kane, A Trai U Blei: bad to ai ka ïing u shakri jong me ba yn kyrkhu ïa ka junom da ka jingkyrkhu jong me.”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hadien kane te u Dabid u la shoh ïa ki Philistia, bad u la jop ïa ki: bad u Dabid u la knieh noh ïa ka Metheg-ammah na ka kti ki Philistia.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la shoh ïa ki Moab, bad u la thew ïa ki da u ksai, u da pynthiah ïa ki ha khyndew; ïa ka ban pynïap u la thew da ar tylli ki ksai, ïa ka ban ri im te u la thew da uwei u ksai shilynter. Bad kita ki Moab ki la long ki khun kliarwait, bad kiba ai khrong ha u Dabid.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Dabid u la shoh ruh ïa u Hadadeser u khun u Rehob, u syiem ka Sobah, mynba u dang leit ïa ka ban knieh noh ïa la ka hima hajan ka Wah Ïuphratis.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Dabid u la kem na u, shi hajar hynñiewspah ki nongshong kulai, bad arphew hajar ki shipai ba ïaleh na tbian: bad u Dabid u la ot ïa ki thied khohwah jong ki kulai ki kali ïapom baroh, hynrei, u la pynsah na ki, shispah tylli ïa ki kali ïapom.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad haba ki Syria kiba na Damaskos ki la ïawan ban ïarap ïa u Hadadeser u syiem ka Sobah, u Dabid u la pynïap na ki Syria, arphew ar hajar ki rangbah.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hangta u Dabid u la buh ïa ki karod ha Syria jong ka Damaskos: te kita ki Syria ki la long ki khun kliarwait ha u Dabid, bad kiba ai khrong. Bad U Trai u la ai ka jingjop ïa u Dabid kat shaba u la leit.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Dabid u la shim noh ïa kita ki 'tieh ksiar ruh kiba ha ki shakri u Hadadeser, bad u la wallam ïa ki sha Jerusalem.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad na Betah ruh bad na Berothai, ki nongbah jong u Hadadeser, u syiem Dabid u la wallam shikatdei eh ka tama.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Haba u Toi u syiem ka Hamath u la ïohsngew ba u Dabid u la shoh jop ïa u paidïapom u Hadadeser baroh,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> hangta te u Toi u la phah ïa u Joram u khun jong u sha u syiem Dabid, ïa ka ban khublei ïa u, bad ban kyrkhu ïa u, namar ba u la ïaleh thma ïa u Hadadeser bad ba u la jop noh ïa u: naba u Hadadeser u la shait ïaleh thma ïa u Toi. Bad u Joram u la wallam lem bad u, ïa ki pliang rupa, bad ïa ki pliang ksiar, bad ïa ki pliang tama de:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ïa kine ruh, u syiem Dabid u la pynkyntang ha U Trai, lem bad kata ka rupa bad kata ka ksiar ïa kaba u la pynkyntang kaba na kita ki jaid bynriew baroh ïa kiba u la jop noh:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> kaba na ki Syria, bad na ki Moab, bad na ki khun u Ammon, bad na ki Philistia, bad na ki Amalek, bad na kata ka jinglute kaba na u Hadadeser, u khun u Rehob, u syiem ka Sobah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad la kyntiew nam ïa u Dabid, haba u la wan phai noh na kaba pynïap ïa ki Syria ha ka Them ka Mluh, kata jin khatphra hajar ngut ki briew.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u la buh ki karod ha ka ri Edom; ha ka ri Edom baroh kawei keiñ u la buh ki karod, bad ki Edom baroh ki la long ki khun kliarwait ha u Dabid. U Trai te u la ai ka jingjop ïa u Dabid kat shaba u la leit.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Dabid u la synshar halor ki Israel baroh: bad u Dabid u la leh ïa ka jingbishar bad ïa ka hok ïa ki briew jong u baroh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u Joab u khun ka Seruïah u la long halor u paidïapom; bad u Jehoshaphat u khun u Ahilud u la long uba thoh pynkynmaw:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad u Sadok u khun u Ahitub, bad u Ahimelekh u khun u Abiathar, ki la long ki lyngdoh; bad u Seraïah u la long u nongthoh;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada u la long halor ki Khereth bad ki Peleth ruh; te ki khun shynrang u Dabid ki la long ki bakhraw batri."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong, “Dang don ne em uno uno ïa uba la pynsah na ka ïing u Saul, ba ngan ïoh leh isynei ïa u na ka bynta u Jonathan?”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te la don u shakri uwei uba na ka ïing u Saul uba ka kyrteng “u Siba”, bad haba ki la khot ïa u sha u Dabid, u syiem u la kylli ïa u, “Ma me u Siba?” U ruh u la ïathuh, “U shakri jong me long uta keiñ.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u syiem u la kylli, “Don ne em uno uno uba dang sah na ka ïing u Saul, ba ngan ïoh leh ïa ka jingisynei U Blei ïa u?” Te u Siba u la ïathuh ha u syiem, “Dang sah sa uwei u khun u jong u Jonathan, u ba-dkoh ki kjat.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u syiem u la kylli ïa u, “U hangno?” U Siba te u la ïathuh ha u syiem, “Ha khmih, u ha ka ïing u Makhir u khun u Ammiel, ha Lo-debar.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid syiem u la phah, bad u la wallam ïa u na ka ïing u Makhir u khun u Ammiel, na Lo-debar.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba u Mephibosheth, u khun u Jonathan, u khun u Saul, u la wan ha u Dabid, u la dem ngon, bad u la nguh de. Bad u Dabid u la ong, “Mephibosheth.” U ruh u la ïathuh, “Ha khmih u shakri jong me!”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong ha u, “Wat sheptieng: naba ngan leh isynei keiñ ïa me shisha na ka bynta u Jonathan u kpa jong me, bad ngan ai noh pat ha me ïa ka khyndew baroh ka jong u Saul u kpa jong me; bad men ïoh bam kpu ha ka miej jong nga ha la ka sngi.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U ruh u la nguh, bad u la ong, “U shakri jong me u long aïu, haba me khmih ïa nga uba kum u ksew u baïap?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem u la khot ïa u Siba, u shakri u Saul, bad u la ong ha u, “Ïa kita kiei kiei baroh kiba la dei ki jong u Saul bad ki jong ka ïing jong u baroh nga la aiti noh ha u khun u kynrad jong me.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ma me te, bad ki khun shynrang jong me, bad ki shakri jong me, phin rep ïa kata ka khyndew na ka bynta jong u; bad men wallam shapoh ïa ka jingmih, khnang ba u khun u kynrad jong me un ïoh kpu ba un bam: hynrei, u Mephibosheth u khun u kynrad jong me un bam kpu ha la ka sngi ha ka miej jong nga.” U Siba te u la don khatsan ngut ki khun shynrang, bad arphew ngut ki shakri.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta, u Siba u la ong ha u syiem, “Katba kum kita kiei kiei baroh ba u syiem kynrad jong nga u la hukum ïa la u shakri, kumta u shakri jong me un leh keiñ.” “U Mephibosheth te”, u la ong u syiem, “un ïoh bam jingbam ha ka miej jong nga, kumjuh kum uwei na ki khun u syiem.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U Mephibosheth te u la don u khun uba dang khynnah, uba ka kyrteng jong u, “u Mikah”. Bad baroh kat kiba shong ha ïing u Siba ki la long ki shakri ïa u Mephibosheth.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kumta, u Mephibosheth u la shong duh ha Jerusalem: naba u la bam jingbam ha la ka sngi ha ka miej u syiem: te u ba-dkoh na ki kjat jong u baroh ar."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hadien kane te, u syiem ki khun u Ammon u la ïap, bad u Hanun u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong, “Ngan leh bha ïa u Hanun u khun u Nahash, kumjuh kumba u kpa jong u, u la leh bha ïa nga ruh.” Kumta, u Dabid u la phah ha la ki shakri ïa ka ban pyntngen ïa u shaphang u kpa jong u. Bad ki shakri u Dabid ki la poi sha ka ri ki khun u Ammon.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ki bakhraw batri ki khun u Ammon ki la ïa-ong ha u Hanun u kynrad jong ki, “Me tharai ba u Dabid u pyndonburom ïa u kpa jong me, namar ba u la phah ki nongpyntngen sha me? ym long pynban ïa ka ban jngoh ïa ka shnong, bad ban syntiat ïa ka, bad ban pynjot ïa ka, ba u Dabid u la phah ïa la ki shakri sha me?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kumta, u Hanun u la shim ïa ki shakri u Dabid, bad u la khi mar shiliang na ki 'ñiuh tmoh jong ki, bad u la ot marshiteng ïa ki jaiñ jong ki, haduh ki skhep jong ki, bad u la phah noh ïa ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Haba la ïathuh ïa kane ha u Dabid, u la phah tan ïa ki; naba kita ki briew ki la lehrain eh. Bad u syiem u la ong, “To sah ha Jerikho haduh ba ki la san ki 'ñiuh tmoh jong phi, hadien kata te, sa wan phai noh.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba ki khun u Ammon ki la ïohi ba u Dabid u la isih ïa ki, ki khun u Ammon ki la phah wer ïa ki Syria na Beth-rehob, bad ïa ki Syria na Sobah arphew hajar kiba ïaleh na tbian, bad ïa u syiem ka Maakah shi hajar ki briew, bad ïa ki nong Tob khat-ar hajar ki briew.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad haba u Dabid u la ïohsngew, u la phah ïa u Joab, bad baroh u paidïapom ki rangbah badonbor.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki khun u Ammon ki la lah ïamih noh, bad ki la ïabuh ryntih ïa ka jingïaleh ha khmat ka khyrdop: te ki Syria kiba na Sobah, bad na Rehob, bad ki nong Tob, bad ki nong Maakah, ki la long kyrpang hi ha ka lyngkha.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Haba u Joab u la ïohi ba ka thma ka la long pyrshah ïa u na shakhmat bad na shadien, u la jied na kita kiba la kynsai jong ki Israel baroh, bad u la buh ryntih ïa ki ban ïaleh ïa ki Syria:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad ïa kita kiwei, u la ai ha ka kti u Abishai u para jong u, bad u la buh ryntih ïa ki, ban ïaleh ïa ki khun u Ammon.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u la ong, “Lada ki Syria kin lah ïa nga, ma me to men ïarap ïa nga: hynrei, lada ki khun u Ammon kin lah ïa me, te nga ngan wan ïarap ïa me.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> To long shlur, bad ngin leh rangbah na ka bynta u paidbah jong ngi; bad na ka bynta ki nongbah U Blei jong ngi: bad U Trai to un leh katba u ibit hi.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kumta, u Joab bad uta u paid uba la don bad u ki la leit hajan ïa ka ban ïaleh thma ïa ki Syria: ki te ki la phet ïap ha khmat jong u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad haba ki khun u Ammon ki la ïohi ba ki Syria ki la phet ïap, ki ruh ki la phet ïap ha khmat u Abishai, bad ki la rung shapoh shnong. Ynda kumta, u Joab u la leit wan noh na ki khun u Ammon, bad u la poi sha Jerusalem.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te haba ki Syria ki la ïohi ba la jop ïa ki ha khmat ki Israel, ki la ïalum khar paid.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Hadareser u la phah, bad u la wallam ïa kita ki Syria kiba sha shiliang kata ka Wah: bad ki la ïawan sha Helam, bad u Shobakh u kaptan u paidïapom u Hadareser ha shuwa jong ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad la pyntip ïa u Dabid; u ruh u la lum khar paid ïa ki Israel baroh, bad u la leit sha shiliang ka Jordan, bad u la poi ha Helam. Bad ki Syria ki la ïabuh ryntih ïa lade pyrshah ïa u Dabid, bad ki la ïaleh thma ïa u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ki Syria te ki la ïaphet ïap ha khmat ki Israel; bad na ki Syria, u Dabid u la pynïap ïa ki rangbah jong ki hynñiewspah tylli ki kali ïapom, bad sawphew hajar ki nongshong kulai, bad u la shoh ïa u Shobakh u kaptan ki paidïapom jong ki, kumta u la ïap hangta.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te haba kita ki syiem baroh kiba la long ki shakri ïa u Hadareser ki la ïohi ba la pynïap ïa ki ha khmat ki Israel, ki la ïasuk noh bad ki Israel, bad ki la shakri ïa ki. Kumta, ki Syria ki la sheptieng ban ïarap shuh ïa ki khun u Ammon."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ynda ha kawei ka snem, ha ka aïom ba ki syiem ki ju leit mih ban ïaleh thma, u Dabid u la phah ïa u Joab, lem bad ki shakri jong u, bad ki Israel baroh de; ki ruh ki la pynjot noh ïa ki khun u Ammon, bad ki la ker kut ïa ka Rabbah. Hynrei, u Dabid u la sah ha Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ka la jia te ha kawei ka janmiet, ba u Dabid u la khie na la ka jingthiah bad u la ïaid kai hajrong ïing ka ïing u syiem: bad na jrong ïing, u la ïohi ïa ka kynthei ba ka da sum; te kata ka kynthei ka la long kaba bhabriew eh ban khmih ïa ka.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Dabid u la phah kylli shaphang kata ka kynthei. Te uwei u la ong, “Kane kam long ka Bathsheba, ka khun u Eliam, ka tnga u Uriah u kynja Hit?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Dabid u la phah ki nongkit-ktien, bad u la shim ïa ka; ka ruh ka la wan shapoh sha u, u ruh u la thiah bad ka; (naba la pynkhuid ïa ka na ka jingpang jong ka;) te ka la leit wan noh sha la ïing.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kata ka kynthei te ka la punkhun; bad ka la phah ïathuh ha u Dabid, bad ka la ong, “Nga la punkhun.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Dabid u la phah sha u Joab u da ong, “To phah sha nga ïa u Uriah u kynja Hit.” U Joab te u la phah ïa u Uriah sha u Dabid.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba u Uriah u la wan sha u, u Dabid u la kylli ïa u, u Joab u kumno, bad kumno u paidbah, bad kumno ka ïaid ka thma.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong ïa u Uriah, “Khie leit hiar sha la ïing, bad sait ïa la ki sla'jat.” Bad u Uriah u la leit mih noh na ka ïing u syiem, bad la phah lam ka jingbam na u syiem hadien jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, u Uriah u la thiah ha ka jingkhang ka ïing u syiem ryngkat bad ki shakri u kynrad jong u baroh bad um shym leit hiar sha la ïing.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba ki la ïathuh ha u Dabid, da kaba ong, “U Uriah um shym leit hiar sha la ïing,” u Dabid u la ong ha u Uriah, “Balei, mem shym wan na la ka jingleit? Hato kumno ba mem shym leit hiar sha la ïing?”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Uriah u la ong ha u Dabid, “Kata ka Synduk ka Jutang, bad ki Israel, bad ki Judah, ki ïashong ha ka ïingtrep; bad u kynrad jong nga u Joab, bad ki shakri u kynrad jong nga, ki ïashong dara shabar ha madan; nga kumno ngan leit sha la ïing, ban bam bad ban dih, bad ban thiah bad la ka tnga? Katba me im, bad katba ka im ka mynsiem jong me, ngan ym leh kum ïa kane ka kam.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong ïa u Uriah, “To shong shane sa kane ka sngi, lashai te ngan pyllait noh ïa me.” Kumta, u Uriah u la sah ha Jerusalem kata ka sngi bad lashai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U Dabid te u la khot ïa u, ban bam bad ban dih ha khmat jong u; bad u la pynbuaid ïa u: bad ynda miet u la leit thiah ha la ka jingthiah lem bad ki shakri u kynrad jong u, hynrei, um shym leit hiar sha la ïing.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Mynstep te u Dabid u la thoh shithi sha u Joab, bad u la phah ïa ka ha ka kti u Uriah.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ha kata ka shithi u la thoh, u da ong, “To buh ïa u Uriah ha pyrshah kaba jur tam ka jingïaleh, bad kynriah noh na u, khnang ba yn shoh ïa u, bad ba un ïap noh.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te mynba u Joab u ap tawiar ïa kata ka shnong, u la buh ïa u Uriah ha ka jaka kaba u tip ba la don ki rangbah kiba shlur.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki rangbah jong kata ka shnong ki la ïamih shabar, bad ki la ïaleh ïa u Joab: bad katto katne na u paidbah, ki shakri u Dabid, ki la ïakyllon ïap; bad u Uriah u kynja Hit ruh u la ïap.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joab u la phah ïathuh ha u Dabid ïa kiei kiei baroh shaphang ka thma;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad u la hukum ïa uta u nonglam-ktien, da kaba ong, “Haba me la pyndep ban ïathuh ïa kiei kiei baroh shaphang ka thma ha u syiem,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> te lada ka jingbitar u syiem kan khih, bad lada un ong ha me, ‘Balei phi la leit hajan katta katta ïa ka shnong ban ïaleh? hato phim shym tip ba kin siat nalor ka kynroh?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Uei ba la shoh ïap ïa u Abimelekh u khun u Jerubbesheth? Ym dei ka kynthei kaba la pynnoh halor jong u da shi dkhot u mawtylliat nalor ki kynroh, kumta u la ïap ha Thebes? Balei phi la leit hajan kata ka kynroh?’ ynda kumta, men ong, ‘U Uriah u kynja Hit u shakri jong me u ruh u la ïap.’ ”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumta, uta u nonglam-ktien u la leit, bad u la wan ïathuh ha u Dabid ïa kita baroh ba u Joab u la phah ïa u shaphang jong ki.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad uta u nonglam-ktien u la ong ha u Dabid, “Shisha kita ki briew ki la jop ïa ngi, bad ki la mih noh sha ngi ha madan, ngi ruh ngi la beh nadien jong ki haduh ka jingkhang ka khyrdop.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ki nongsiat ki la siat sha ki shakri jong me nalor kata ka kynroh; te na ki shakri u syiem don kiba la ïap, bad u Uriah u kynja Hit u shakri jong me ruh u la ïap.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la ong ha uta u nonglam-ktien, “Kumne men ong ha u Joab. ‘Wat ai ba kane kan pynsngewsih ïa me, naba ka waitlam kan pynjot noh ïa une bad ïa uta kumjuh: to nang pynjur ïa la ka jingïaleh thma pyrshah ïa ka shnong, bad to pynjot ïa ka’: ma me ruh to men pynshlur ïa u.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te haba ka tnga u Uriah ka la ïohsngew ba u la ïap u Uriah u tnga jong ka, ka la ïambriew ïa la u tnga.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad haba la kut kata ka jingïambriew, u Dabid u la phah shaw ïa ka sha ka ïing jong u, bad ka la long ka tnga jong u, bad ka la kha u khun ïa u. Hynrei, kata ka kam kaba u Dabid u la leh, ka la pynsngewsih ïa U Trai."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la phah ïa u Nathan sha u Dabid. U la wan te sha u, bad u la ong ha u, “Ki la don ar ngut ki briew ha kawei ka shnong; uwei u riewspah, bad uta uwei u duk.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Uta u bariewspah te u la don shibun eh ki langbrot bad ki masi:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> hynrei, uta u baduk um shym don ei ei, hynrei, tang iwei i khun langbrot iba rit ïa iba u la thied bad ba u la bsa; te i la nang san lem bad u, bad lem bad ki khun jong u; na ka jingbam jong u i la ju bam, bad na ka khuri jong u i la ju dih, bad ha ka shadem jong u i la ju thiah, bad i la long ha u kum ka khun.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u nongleit jingleit u la wan ha uta u bariewspah, hynrei, u la bynnud ban shim na la ki jong ki langbrot bad na la ki jong ki masi, ïa ka ban khreh na ka bynta uta u nongleit jingleit uba la wan ha u, hynrei, u shim ïa ita i khun langbrot uta u briew u baduk, bad u la khreh ïa ka na ka bynta uta u briew uba la wan ha u.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ka jingbitar u Dabid ka la meh lep ïa uta u briew; bad u la ong ha u Nathan, “Katba im U Trai, uta u briew uba la leh ïa kane u dei shisha ban ïap:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad un pynburia saw shah na ka bynta ita i khun langbrot, namar ba u la leh ïa kane ka kam, bad ba um shym la sngewsynei.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Nathan te u la ong ha u Dabid, “Me long ma me uta u briew. Kumne u ong U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ‘Nga la pynsleh ïa me ban long u syiem halor ki Israel, nga la pynim ruh ïa me na ka kti u Saul;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad nga la ai ha me ïa ka ïing u kynrad jong me, bad ïa ki tnga u kynrad jong me ha ka shadem jong me, bad nga la ai ha me ïa ka ïing u Israel bad ïa ka jong u Judah; bad lada kata ka la kham khyndiat, ngan da la ai kham bun shikatdei.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Balei te me la beiñ ïa ka ktien U Trai, ïa ka ban leh sniew ha khmat jong u? Ïa u Uriah u kynja Hit me la pynïap da ka waitlam, bad ïa ka tnga jong u me la shim ban long ka tnga jong me, bad me la pynïap ïa u da ka waitlam ki khun u Ammon.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Mynta te namar kata, ka waitlam kan ym iehnoh ïa ka ïing jong me lano lano ruh; namar ba me la beiñ ïa nga, bad ba me la shim ïa ka tnga u Uriah, u kynja Hit ban long ka tnga jong me.’",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kumne u ong U Trai, ‘Ha khmih, ngan pynmih ïa ka jingsniew pyrshah ïa me na ka ïing jong me hi, bad ngan shim ïa ki tnga jong me ha khmat jong me, bad ngan ai ïa ki ha u paramarjan jong me, u ruh un thiah bad ki tnga jong me ha pyrshah kane ka sngi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Naba me la leh ïa ka ha kaba rieh: hynrei, nga ngan leh ïa kane ka jingleh ha khmat ki Israel baroh, bad ha pyrshah ka sngi.’ ”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Nathan, “Nga la leh pop ïa U Trai.” U Nathan te u la ïathuh ha u Dabid, “U Trai ruh u la pyndam noh ïa kata ka pop jong me; men ym ïap keiñ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Pynban, namar ba da kane ka jingleh me la ai ka daw kaba khraw ïa ki nongshun jong U Trai ban krenbeiñ blei, ita i khynnah ruh iba la kha ïa me in ïap shisha.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Nathan u la leit noh sha la ïing. Bad U Trai u la shoh ïa ita i khynnah iba la kha ka tnga u Uriah ïa u Dabid, te i la pang eh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U Dabid, namar kata, u la kyrpad ïa U Blei na ka bynta ita i khynnah; bad u Dabid u la shah jingit, bad u la leit, bad u la thiah ha khyndew baroh shi miet.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ki tymmen basan ka ïing jong u ki la mih, bad ki la ïeng hajan jong u, ïa ka ban pynïeng ïa u na khyndew: u te um treh, lymne um bam kpu lem bad ki.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew te ita i khynnah i la ïap. Hynrei, ki shakri u Dabid ki la sheptieng ban ïathuh ha u ba i la ïap i khynnah: namar ki la ïa-ong, “Ha khmih, katba i khynnah i dang im, ngi la kren ha u, hynrei, um sngap ïa ka ktien jong ngi: katno te ba un pynkhuslai ïa lade, lada ngin ïathuh ha u ba i la ïap i khynnah?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, haba u Dabid u la ïohi ïa la ki shakri ba ki ïakren pasiaw, u Dabid u la sngewthuh ba i la ïap i khynnah: kumta, u Dabid u la kylli ïa la ki shakri, “I la ïap i khynnah?” Ki ruh ki la ïathuh, “I la ïap.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la ïeng na ka khyndew, bad u la sum, bad u la sleh, bad u la pli ïa la ki jaiñ; bad u la wan sha ka ïing U Trai, bad u la mane: hadien kata, u la wan sha la ka jong ka ïing; bad haba u la pan ki la buh kpu ha khmat jong u, u ruh u la bam.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ynda kumta, ki shakri jong u ki la ong ha u, “Kaei kane ba me la leh? Katba i dang im i khynnah, me la shah jingit bad me la ïam na ka bynta jong i; hynrei, ynda i la ïap i khynnah, me la ïeng bad me la bam kpu.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U te u la ïathuh, “Mynba i dang im keiñ i khynnah, nga la shah jingit bad nga la ïam: naba nga la ong, ‘Uei uba lah ban tip la un isynei ne em U Trai ïa nga, ba in ïoh im i khynnah?’",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, mynta i la ïap, ïa ka ban lei pat ngan da shah jingit? Nga lah ma nga ban wallam noh ïa i pat? Ma nga ngan leit sha i, hynrei, ma i in ym wan phai sha nga.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Dabid u la pyntngen ïa ka Bathsheba ka tnga jong u, bad u la bsut sha ka, bad u la thiah bad ka: ka ruh ka la kha ïa u khun, bad u la khot kyrteng “u Solomon” ïa u. Bad U Trai u la ieit ïa u;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> bad u la phah da ka kti u Nathan u nongïathuhlypa, bad u la kyrteng “u Jedidiah” ïa u, na ka bynta U Trai.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u Joab u la ïaleh ïa ka Rabbah ki khun u Ammon, bad u la jop ïa ka nongbah u syiem.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u Joab u la phah ki nonglam-ktien sha u Dabid, bad u la ong, “Nga la ïaleh thma ïa ka Rabbah, bad nga la jop ïa ka shnong ki um.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Mynta te namar kata, to lum lang ïa kiba dang sah na u paidbah, bad to ïaleh ïa ka shnong, bad jop ïa ka: ïoh haba nga la jop ma nga ïa ka shnong, ngan kyrteng ïa ka ha ka kyrteng jong nga.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u Dabid u la lum lang ïa u paidbah baroh, bad u la leit sha Rabbah, bad u la ïaleh ïa ka, bad u la jop ïa ka.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u la shim ïa ka pansngiat u syiem jong ki na ka khlieh jong u; te ka jingkhia jong ka, ka la don shi talent ksiar, bad ki la don ha ka ki mawkordor; bad la buh ïa ka ha ka khlieh u Dabid. U la shim noh ruh shikatdei ka jinglute na kata ka shnong.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u la leit lam noh ïa ki briew kiba ha ka, bad u la buh ïa ki ha ki kurat, bad ha ki nar puh, bad ha ki sdie nar, bad u la pyntrei ïa ki ha ki pajwa maw-it: bad kumta, u la leh ha ki shnong ki khun u Ammon baroh. Kumta u Dabid bad u paidbah baroh ki la leit phai pat sha Jerusalem."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te hadien kane, u Absalom u khun u Dabid u la don ka para kaba bhabriew, kaba kyrteng “ka Tamar”: bad u Amnon u khun u Dabid u la ieit ïa ka.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Amnon u la sngewsih katta katta ba u la pang namar ka Tamar ka para jong u; namar ka la long ka theisotti: te u Amnon um shym idon lad ban leh ei ei ïa ka.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hynrei, u Amnon u la don u lok, uba kyrteng “u Jonadab”, u khun u Shimeah u hynmen u Dabid: bad u Jonadab u la long u briew u basian eh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u la ong ha u, “Ma me u khun u syiem, balei ba me nang raikhoh nang raikhoh ha la ka sngi? Mem ïathuh ha nga?” U Amnon te u la ïathuh ha u, “Nga ieit keiñ ïa ka Tamar, ka para u Absalom u para jong nga.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Jonadab u la ong ha u, “To thiah keiñ ha la ka jingthiah, bad leh mynleh pang ïa lade: te haba u kpa jong me u wan jngoh ïa me, to ong ha u, ‘Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ïa ka Tamar ka para jong nga ba kan wan ai jingbam ïa nga, bad ban khreh jingbam ha khmat jong nga, ba ngan ïohi, bad ïoh bam ïa ka na ka kti jong ka.’ ”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta, u Amnon u la thiah bad u la leh mynleh pang ïa lade: bad haba u syiem u la wan jngoh ïa u, u Amnon u la ong ha u syiem, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ïa ka Tamar ka para jong nga ba kan wan shet ar tylli ki kpu ha khmat jong nga, ba ngan ïoh bam na ka kti jong ka.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la phah sha ïing ha ka Tamar, u da ong, “To leit keiñ sha ka ïing u Amnon u hynmen jong pha, bad khreh jingbam ïa u.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumta, ka Tamar ka la leit sha ïing u Amnon u hynmen jong ka; u te u dang thiah. Bad ka la shim shi lynglun, bad ka la khñiot ïa ka, bad ka la thaw kpu ha khmat jong u, bad ka la shet ïa kita ki kpu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ka la shim da ka nar sdieh, bad ka la theh ïa ki ha khmat jong u; hynrei, um treh ban bam. Bad u Amnon u la ong, “To beh noh shabar ïa ki briew baroh na nga.” Te u briew baroh u la mih shabar na u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Amnon u la ong ïa ka Tamar, “To wallam ïa kata ka jingbam shapoh kane ka kamra, ba ngan dup bam na ka kti jong pha.” Ka Tamar te ka la shim ïa kita ki kpu kiba ka la khreh, bad ka la leit lam shapoh ka kamra ha u Amnon u hynmen jong ka.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te haba ka la leit lam ïa ki hajan jong u ba un ïoh bam, u la bat ïa ka, bad u la ong ha ka, “Ale, ko para jong nga, thiah bad nga.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ka te ka la ïathuh ha u, “Ynnai, ko kong, wat pynkheiñ burom ïa nga; namar ym bit ban leh kaba kum kane ha Israel: wat leh keiñ kum kane ka jingleh bieit.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nga ruh ngan kit shaei ïa la ka jinglehrain? ma me te men long kum uwei na ki riewbieit ha Israel. Mynta namar kata te, nga kyrpad ïa me, to ïakren bad u syiem; naba un ym adong ïa nga ha me.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> La kumta ruh, um treh ban sngap ïa ka ktien jong ka; hynrei, ba u kham khlaiñ ïa ka, u la leh jubor ïa ka, bad u la thiah bad ka.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ynda kumta, u Amnon u la isih ïa ka da ka jingisih ka bakhraw eh; kumta kata ka jingisih da kaba u la isih ïa ka, ka la kham khraw ïa kata ka jingieit da kaba u la ieit ïa ka. Bad u Amnon u la ong ïa ka, “Khie noh, leit noh.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ka te ka la ong ha u, “Ym kumta, namar kane ka jinglehrain kaba khraw ba me beh noh ïa nga ka kham sniew ban ïa kata kawei ba me la leh ïa nga.” Hynrei, um sngap ïa ka.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ynda kumta, u la khot ïa u shakri jong u, uba shakri ïa u, bad u la ong, “To beh noh shabar ïa kane ka briew na nga: bad khang ïa ka jingkhang hadien jong ka.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ka la kup da ka jaiñkup kaba khleh rong: naba la ju pynkup ïa ki khun kynthei kiba dang sotti jong ki syiem ha ki jaiñkup kiba kum kine. Ynda kumta, uta u shakri jong u, u la lam shabar ïa ka bad u la khang ïa ka jingkhang hadien jong ka.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ka Tamar ka la buh da u dpei halor ka khlieh jong ka, bad ka la kad ïa kata ka jaiñkup kaba khleh rong kaba ka kup; bad ka la buh ïa la ka kti halor la ka khlieh, bad ka la leit noh, ka da lynñiar artad ha lynti.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Absalom u hynmen jong ka u la ong ha ka, “U Amnon u hynmen jong pha u la leit sha pha? Hynrei, ko hep, to sngap jar mynta: u long u hynmen jong pha; to wat pynkhuslai la ka dohnud namar kane.” Kumta, ka Tamar ka la sah rangli ha ïing u Absalom u hynmen jong ka.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, haba u syiem Dabid u la ïohsngew ïa kine kiei kiei baroh, u la bitar eh lep.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Absalom te um shym kren ka basniew lymne ka babha ïa u Amnon: naba u Absalom u la shun ïa u Amnon, namar ba u la leh bor ïa ka Tamar ka para jong u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ynda la ar snem biang: u Absalom u la don kiba khap shñiuh langbrot ha Baal-hasor, kaba hajan Ephraim: bad u Absalom u la khot ïa ki khun shynrang u syiem baroh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Absalom u la wan sha u syiem, bad u la ong, “Mynta, ha khmih, u shakri jong me u don kiba khap shñiuh langbrot; nga kyrpad ïa me, to ai ba un wan u syiem bad ki shakri jong u lem bad u shakri jong me.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U syiem te u la ong ha u Absalom, “Em, ko khun, ngin ym leit baroh, ïoh ngi ban khia halor jong me.” U te u la kyrpad eh ïa u: la kumta ruh um treh leit, hynrei, u la kyrkhu ïa u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ynda kumta, u Absalom u la ong, “Lada kumta, nga kyrpad te, to shah ïa u Amnon u hynmen jong nga ban leit lem bad ngi.” U syiem te u la ong ha u, “Ban lei un leit lem bad me?”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, u Absalom u la kyrpad eh ïa u, ba un phah ïa u Amnon bad ki khun shynrang u syiem baroh ryngkat bad u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te u Absalom u la hukum ïa la ki shakri, u da ong, “To khmih thuh te, haba ka dohnud u Amnon ka la kmen da ka Waiñ; bad haba ngan ong ïa phi, ‘To shoh ïa u Amnon’, hangta te to pynïap ïa u, wat sheptieng: balei, ngam shym hukum ïa phi? leh rangbah keiñ, bad to long kiba shlur ruh.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad ki shakri u Absalom ki la leh ïa u Amnon kumba u Absalom u la hukum. Hangta te ki khun shynrang u syiem baroh ki la khie, bad uwei uwei baroh u la shong halor la ka kadda, bad ki la phet ïap.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te mynba ki dang ha lynti, ka jingbna ka wan ha u Dabid, kaba ong, “U Absalom u la pynïap ïa ki khun shynrang u syiem baroh, bad ym don uwei ruh na ki ba la pynsah.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem u la ïeng, bad u la kad ïa la ki jaiñ, bad u la thiah ha ka khyndew; bad ki shakri baroh ki la ïeng hajan kiba la kad ïa la ki jaiñ.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te u Jonadab, u khun u Shimeah u hynmen u Dabid, u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Wat ai ba u kynrad jong nga un tharai ba ki la pynïap ïa kita ki samla baroh kiba ki khun shynrang u syiem; naba tang u Amnon hi u la ïap: naba ïa kane la lah thew lypa da ka jingbuh u Absalom naduh kata ka sngi ba u la leh jubor ïa ka Tamar ka para jong u.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Mynta te wat ai ba u syiem kynrad jong nga un khuslai la ka dohnud namar kane, da kaba tharai ba la ïap ki khun shynrang u syiem baroh: namar tang u Amnon hi u la ïap.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hynrei, u Absalom u la phet ïap. Bad uta u shakri uba ap u la khmied ïa la ki khmat, bad u la khmih, te, ha khmih, ki la wan shibun ki briew na ka lynti ka ranab lum na shadien jong u.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad u Jonadab u la ong ha u syiem, “Ha khmih, kita ki khun u syiem ki ïawan: kumba u shakri jong me u la ong, kumta ka long keiñ.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad haba u dang shu lah kren, ha khmih, kita ki khun u syiem ki la lap ba poi, bad ki la pynjam ïa la ka ktien, bad ki la ïam. Bad u syiem ruh bad ki shakri jong u baroh ki la ïam da ka jinglynñiar ka bakhraw eh.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Hynrei, u Absalom u la phet ïap, bad u la leit sha u Talmai u khun u Ammihud, u syiem ka Geshur. U Dabid te u la ïambriew ïa la u khun ha la ka sngi.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Kumta, u Absalom u la phet ïap, bad u la leit sha Geshur, bad u la sah hangta lai snem.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te ka mynsiem u syiem Dabid ka la kwah eh ban leit mih sha u Absalom: naba la pyntngen ïa u namar u Amnon, haba u la lah ïap."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Joab u khun ka Seruïah u la tip ba ka dohnud u syiem ka la phai sha u Absalom.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Joab u la phah sha Tekoa, bad u la wallam nangta ïa kawei ka briew kaba sian, bad u la ong ha ka, “Nga kyrpad ïa pha, to leh mynleh kaba ïambriew ïa lade, bad to kup da ki jaiñ sngewsih, bad wat sleh ïa lade da ka umphniang, hynrei, to long kum ka briew kaba ïambriew la slem ïa u baïap;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad to leit ruh sha u syiem, bad kren ha u da kine ki ktien.” Kumta u Joab u la buh ïa kine ki ktien ha ka shyntur jong ka.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te haba kata ka briew kaba na Tekoa ka la kren ha u syiem, ka la dem ngon la ka khmat haduh khyndew, bad ka la nguh de, bad ka la ong, “Ko syiem, to ïarap.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U syiem te u la ong ha ka, “Ka la jia aïu ïa pha?” Ka ruh ka la ïathuh, “Da shisha nga long ka riewkynthei, bad u tnga jong nga u la ïap.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ka shakri jong me ka la don ar ngut ki khun shynrang, bad kine ar ngut ki la ïashoh ha lyngkha, bad ym shym don mano mano ban pynkhlad ïa ki, te uwei u la shoh ïa uta uwei, bad u la pynïap noh ïa u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te, ha khmih, ki kur baroh ki la ïeng ïaleh ïa ka shakri jong me, bad ki la ïa-ong, ‘To ai noh ïa uba la pynïap ïa la u para, ba ngi ruh ngin pynïap ïa u na ka bynta ka jingim uta u para jong u ïa uba u la pynïap, bad kumta ngin pynjot noh ïa uta u nongïoh pateng ruh’: kumta kin pynlip noh ïa u rnga ding jong nga ïa uba la pynsah, bad kin ym pynsah nam lymne ki khun ki ksiew ïa u tnga jong nga ha khmat ka pyrthei.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u syiem u la ong ha kata ka briew, “To khie leit sha la ïing, ngan sa pynmih hukum shaphang jong pha.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te kata ka briew kaba na Tekoa ka la ong ha u syiem, “To kane ka pop kan long halor jong nga, bad halor ka ïing u kpa jong nga, ko syiem kynrad: u syiem te bad ka khet jong u kin khuid.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u syiem u la ong, “Uno uno ruh u ban kren ei ei ïa pha, to wallam ïa u sha nga, te uta un ym ïoh ktah shuh ïa pha.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta, ka la ong, “Nga kyrpad, to u syiem un kynmaw ïa U Trai uba U Blei jong me, ba u nongpynhiar kput ka snam un ym nang pynjot shuh shuh, ïoh kin pynjot noh ïa u khun jong nga.” U te u la ïathuh, “Katba im U Trai, iwei i 'ñiuh khlieh jong u khun jong pha in ym hap ha ka khyndew.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ynda kumta, kata ka kynthei ka la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ïa ka shakri jong me ban kren shikyntien ha u syiem kynrad.” U ruh u la ong, “To kren.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te kata ka briew ka la ong, “Namar kata te balei ba me la pyrkhat kumne pyrshah ïa u paidbah jong U Blei? namar haba u syiem u kren ïa kane ka ktien u long kum uba rem, ha kaba u syiem um wallam pat sha la ïing ïa uba la beh noh jong u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Naba ngi dei ban ïap noh, bad ngi long kum ka um ba la theh ha khyndew, ïa kaba ym lah shuh ban tong pat; lymne U Blei um shim noh ïa ka jingim, hynrei, u pyrkhat ïa ka lad ba uta ïa uba la beh noh un ym long uba la kyntait noh na u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Namar kata te, nga la wan ban kren ha u syiem kynrad ïa kane ka ktien, namar ba u paidbah u la pynsheptieng ïa nga: kumta ka shakri jong me ka la ong, ‘Ngan ïakren te bad u syiem; lehse u syiem un leh ïa ka jingkyrpad ka shakri jong u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Naba u syiem un sngap, ïa ka ban pyllait ïa ka shakri jong u na ka kti jong uta u briew uba la thew ban pynjot noh ïa nga lem bad u khun jong nga na kata ka bynta trai jong U Blei.’",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ka shakri jong me te ka la ong, ‘Nga kyrpad ïa me, to ka ktien u syiem kynrad kan long ïa ka ban pyntngen’: naba u syiem kynrad u long kum u angel U Blei, ïa ka ban sngap ïa ka babha bad ïa ka basniew: bad U Trai U Blei jong me to un long lem bad me.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha kata ka briew, “Nga kyrpad ïa pha, to wat buhrieh ei ei na kane kaba ngan sa kylli ïa pha.” Te kata ka kynthei ka la ong, “To un kren te u syiem kynrad jong nga.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u syiem u la ong, “Ka kti u Joab ka don lem ne em bad pha ha kane baroh?” Te kata ka kynthei ka la ïathuh bad ka la ong, “Katba im ka mynsiem jong me, ko syiem kynrad, ym lah ban phai sha kamon lymne sha kadiang na kiei kiei baroh ba u syiem kynrad u la ong: naba u shakri jong me u Joab u la hukum ïa nga, bad u la buh ma u ïa kine ki ktien baroh ha ka shyntur ka shakri jong me:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ïa ka ban pynphai ïa kane ka kam ba u shakri jong me u Joab u la leh khnang ïa kane: hynrei, u kynrad jong nga u long uba stad, kum ka jingstad u angel U Blei, ïa ka ban tip ïa kiei kiei baroh kiba ha ka pyrthei.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U syiem te u la ong ha u Joab, “Ha khmih te, nga la leh ïa kane ka kam: khie leit, bad wallam pat ïa uta u samla u Absalom.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Joab u la dem ngon la ka khmat, bad u la nguh, bad u la kyrkhu ïa u syiem. Bad u Joab u la ong, “Ha kane ka sngi, u shakri jong me u tip ba nga la shem ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong me, ko syiem kynrad, namar ba u syiem u la leh ïa ka jingkyrpad u shakri jong u.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u Joab u la ïeng bad u la leit sha Geshur, bad u la wallam ïa u Absalom sha Jerusalem.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U syiem te u la ong, “To un phai sha la ka jong ka ïing, hynrei, un ym ïohi ïa ka khmat jong nga.” Kumta, u Absalom u la phai sha la ka jong ka ïing, bad um shym ïohi ïa ka khmat u syiem.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te kat u Absalom ha Israel baroh ym shym don uba ïoh ïaroh namar ka jingbhabriew jong u: naduh ka sla'jat jong u haduh ka lyngkyrwiang khlieh jong u ym shym don jingduna ha u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad haba u la khi ïa la ka khlieh, (naba u la ju khi ïa la u shñiuh shi sien shi snem: namar ba u khia eh halor jong u, namar kata, u la ju khi ïa u:) u la ju thew ïa u 'ñiuh khlieh jong u arspah shekel, ha ka jingthew u syiem.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te ïa u Absalom la kha lai ngut ki khun shynrang, bad kawei ka kynthei, kaba kyrteng “ka Tamar”: ka la long ka kynthei kaba bhabriew.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta, u Absalom u la shong la dap ar snem ha Jerusalem; bad um shym la ïohi ïa ka khmat u syiem.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Namar kata, u Absalom u la phah khot ïa u Joab, ïa ka ban phah ïa u sha u syiem: hynrei, um treh ban wan ha u: bad u la phah pat ka ba-ar sien, hynrei, um treh wan.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Namar kata, u la ong ïa la ki shakri, “Phi ïohi ïa ka lyngkha u Joab hajan ka jong nga, bad u don hangta u Kew Barli; khie leit keiñ bad wiang ïa ka.” Kumta, ki shakri u Absalom ki la wiang ïa kata ka lyngkha.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joab u la ïeng, bad u la wan sha u Absalom hapoh ïing jong u, bad u la ong ha u, “Ki shakri jong me ki la wiang ïa ka lyngkha jong nga balei?”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> U Absalom te u la ïathuh ha u Joab, “Ha khmih, nga la phah sha me, da kaba ong, ‘Ale shane, ba ngan ïoh phah ïa me sha u syiem, ïa ka ban ong, “Nga la wan noh na Geshur ïa ka ban lei? Ka la kham bha ïa nga ban sah hangto haduh mynta: mynta te, to ai ngan ïohi ïa ka khmat u syiem; bad lada don ka pop ha nga, to un pynïap ïa nga.” ’ ”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Kumta, u Joab u la wan sha u syiem, bad u la ïathuh ha u: te haba u la phah khot ïa u Absalom, u ruh u la wan sha u syiem, bad u la dem ngon la ka khmat haduh khyndew ha khmat u syiem. U syiem te u la doh ïa u Absalom."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hadien kane te, u Absalom u la khreh ïa lade ki kali bad ki kulai, bad sanphew ngut ki briew ïa ka ban phet ha shuwa jong u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Absalom u la ju khie dang step, bad u la ju ïeng harud ka lynti ka khyrdop: te ka la long kumta, ba haba uno uno u briew uba don ka kajia u wan sha u syiem ban ïoh bishar, hangta u Absalom u la ju khot ïa u, bad u ong, “Me uba na kano ka shnong?” Uta te u la ju ïathuh, “U shakri jong me uba na kawei na ki jaid Israel.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Absalom te u la ju ong ïa u, “Ha khmih, ki kam jong me ki babha bad ki bahok; hynrei, ym don mano mano ba la buh da u syiem ban sngap ïa me.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Absalom u la ju ong ruh, “A ban da la buh nongbishar ïa nga ha kane ka ri, ba uno uno u briew uba don ka kam lane ka kajia u lah ban wan ha nga, nga te ngan da leh hok ïa u!”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad haba uno uno u la wan hajan ïa ka ban nguh ïa u, u la ju kner ïa la ka kti, bad u la bat ïa u, bad u doh ïa u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Da kane ka rukom keiñ, u Absalom u la ju leh ïa ki Israel baroh kiba wan sha u syiem ban ïoh bishar. Kumta, u Absalom u la tuh ïa ki dohnud ki rangbah Israel.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ynda la dap sawphew snem, u Absalom u la ong ha u syiem, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ba ngan leit pyndep ha Hebron ïa ka kular jong nga, kaba nga la kular ha U Trai.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Naba u shakri jong me u la kular ïa ka kular mynba nga la shong ha Geshur ha Syria, da kaba ong, ‘Lada shisha U Trai un wallam pat ïa nga sha Jerusalem, nga te ngan shakri ïa U Trai.’ ”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u syiem u la ong ha u, “To leit ha kaba suk.” Kumta u la ïeng, bad u la leit sha Hebron.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, u Absalom u la phah ïa ki nongsyntiat ha ki jaid Israel baroh, da kaba ong, “Phi, tang phi shu ïohsngew ïa ka jingsawa ka ronsing, te hangta phin ong, ‘U Absalom u long syiem ha Hebron.’ ”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki la leit arspah ngut ki rangbah, ïa kiba la khot, lem bad u Absalom na Jerusalem; ki hynrei, ki leit ha kaba lui lui; bad kim shym tip ei ei satia.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Absalom u la phah khot ïa u Ahithophel u nong Gilon, u myntri jong u Dabid, na la ka shnong, kata na Giloh, mynba u dang kñia ïa kita ki jingkñia. Te kata ka jingshetsylla ka la jur; naba u paidbah uba bad u Absalom u la nang bun nang bun.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u nonglam-ktien u la wan ha u Dabid, u da ong, “Ki dohnud ki rangbah Israel ki la snoh ha u Absalom.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong ha la ki shakri baroh kiba la don lem bad u ha Jerusalem, “Ïeng, to ngin ïaphet noh; lymda kumta, ngin ym lait mano mano na u Absalom: to pynkloi ïa ka ban leit, ba ïoh un lap kyndit ïa ngi, bad wallam ka jingjynjar halor jong ngi, bad ba un pom ïa kane ka shnong da ka syrti waitlam.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te kita ki shakri u syiem ki la ïa-ong ha u syiem, “Ha khmih, ki shakri jong me ki la kloi ban leh ïa kiei kiei baroh ba u syiem kynrad jong ngi u mon.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u syiem u la mih noh, bad ki ba-ha-ïing jong u baroh ki bud ïa u. Te u syiem u la iehnoh shiphew ngut ki tnga kliar ïa ka ban sumar ïa ka ïing.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u syiem u la leit noh, bad u paidbah baroh u bud ïa u; te ki la sah ha Beth-merhak.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te kita ki shakri jong u baroh ki la nang ïaid hajan jong u; ki Khereth baroh, bad ki Peleth baroh, bad ki Gitt baroh, hynriewspah ngut ki rangbah kiba la wan bud ïa u na Gath, ki la nang ïaid ha shuwa u syiem.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem u la ong ha u Ittai u nong Gitt, “Balei ba men leit ma me ruh bad ngi? To leit phai noh, bad to shong bad u syiem: naba me long u nongwei, bad ïa uba la beh ruh; to leit phai sha la ka jong ka jaka.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Dang mynhynnin me la wan, te kumno ha kane ka sngi ngan pynïaid sharum shaneng ïa me bad ngi, haba nga shu leit kat shaba lap? To leit phai ma me, bad shim lem ruh ïa la ki para; te ka jingisynei bad ka jingshisha kin long lem bad me.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U Ittai te u la ïathuh ha u syiem, bad u la ong, “Katba im U Trai, bad katba im u syiem kynrad jong nga, shisha shisha ha kata ka jaka kaba u don u syiem kynrad jong nga, la ha kaba ïap lane ha kaba im, hangta hi keiñ u shakri jong me un don ruh.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ïa u Ittai, “Khie da leit te sha shiliang.” Kumta u Ittai u nong Gitt u la leit sha shiliang, bad ki rangbah jong u baroh, bad ki khynnah baroh kiba la don lem bad u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad kata ka ri baroh ka la ïam da ka ktien kaba jam, bad uta u paidbah baroh u la leit sha shiliang: u syiem hi ruh u la leit sha shiliang i wah Kidron, bad u paidbah baroh u la leit sha shiliang, shaphang ka lynti ka ri khlaw.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te, ha khmih, u Sadok ruh, bad ki Lebi baroh kiba la don lem bad u, ki da ïabah ïa ka synduk ka jutang U Blei; bad ki la buh ïa kata ka synduk U Blei ha tbian, bad u Abiathar u la leit kiew, haduh ba u paidbah baroh u la mih noh na kata ka shnong.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U syiem te u la ong ïa u Sadok, “To leit lam noh pat ïa kata ka synduk U Blei sha shnong: lada ngan shem ka jingsngewbha ha khmat U Trai, un pynphai pat ïa nga, bad un pyni ha nga ïa ka ruh, bad ïa ka jaka shong jong u:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> hynrei, lada un ong kumne, ‘Ïa me ngam sngewbha shuh’; ha khmih, nga hangne, to un leh ïa nga katba u ibit ma u.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> U syiem u la ong ruh ha u Sadok lyngdoh, “Me mem long u nongïohi? To phai noh te sha shnong ha kaba suk, bad kita ar ngut ki khun shynrang jong me lem bad me, u Ahimaas, u khun jong me, bad u Jonathan u khun u Abiathar keiñ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ha khmih, ngan shong ha ki khriang ka ri khlaw, haduh ban da poi ktien na phi ïa ka ban pyntip ïa nga.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kumta u Sadok bad u Abiathar ki la bah noh pat ïa kata ka synduk U Blei sha Jerusalem: bad ki la sah ruh hangta.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u Dabid u la leit kiew ïa u lum ki Olib, u da ïam ruh katba kiew artet; bad u la tapmoh ïa la ka khlieh, bad u la ïaid 'jat lyngkhuit ruh de: bad kita ki briew baroh kiba la don lem bad u ki la tapmoh uwei pa uwei ïa la ka khlieh, bad ki la leit artet, ki da ïam katba ki ïakiew.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te la don uba la ïathuh ha u Dabid, da kaba ong, u Ahithophel ruh u don hapdeng kita kiba ïashetsylla bad u Absalom. Bad u Dabid u la ong, “A Trai, nga kyrpad ïa me, to pynkylla jingbieit ïa ka buit sian u Ahithophel.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad haba u Dabid u la poi sha khlieh uta u lum, ha kaba la mane ruh ïa U Blei, ha khmih, u Hushai u nong Arkhi u la wan tan ïa u ba la kad ïa la ka barandi, bad u don ruh ka khyndew halor ka khlieh jong u:",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> te u Dabid u la ong ha u, “Lada men leit sha shiliang bad nga, men shu long jingkit khia halor jong nga:",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> hynrei, lada men leit phai pat sha shnong, bad ba men ong ha u Absalom, ‘Ngan long u shakri jong me, ko syiem; baroh shi katta nga la long u shakri u kpa jong me, mynta te ngan long u shakri jong me’: kumta me lah ban pynduh noh na ka bynta jong nga ïa ka buit sian u Ahithophel.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> U Sadok bad u Abiathar ki lyngdoh keiñ, balei ki ruh kin ym don hangta lem bad me? namar kata, ïa ka ktien baroh kaba men ïohsngew na ka ïing u syiem, to men ïathuh ïa kata ha ki lyngdoh, u Sadok bad u Abiathar keiñ.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ha khmih, ki don hangta lem bad ki, ki khun shynrang jong ki baroh ar ngut, u Ahimaas u khun u Sadok, bad u Jonathan u khun u Abiathar; bad da kita men phah sha nga ïa kaei kaei baroh kaba men ïohsngew.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kumta, u Hushai u lok jong u Dabid u la wan sha shnong; bad u Absalom ruh u la wan sha Jerusalem."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba u Dabid u la palat khyndiat ïa ka khlieh uta u lum, ha khmih, u Siba u shakri u Mephibosheth u la ïashem bad u, u da don ruh shi jur ki kadda ba la teh jin, bad halor kita la don arspah tylli ki kpu, bad shispah rynjup ki soh Khajur, bad shispah tylli ki soh lyiur, bad shi lywa ka Waiñ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u syiem u la ong ha u Siba, “Me mut aïu da kine?” Te u Siba u la ïathuh, “Kine ki kadda ki long ïa ki ba-ha-ïing u syiem ba kin shong halor jong ki; bad kine ki kpu bad ki soh lyiur ïa ki samla ba kin bam; bad kane ka Waiñ ïa kat kiba la thait ha ri khlaw ba kin ïoh dih.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u syiem u la kylli, “Hynrei hangno uta u khun u kynrad jong me?” Bad u Siba u la ïathuh ha u syiem, “Ha khmih, u sah ha Jerusalem keiñ: naba u la ong, ‘Ha kane ka sngi ka ïing Israel kan aiti pat ha nga ïa ka hima u kpa jong nga.’ ”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem u la ong ha u Siba, “Ha khmih, kiei kiei baroh ki jong u Mephibosheth ki long ki jong me.” U Siba te u la ong, “Nga nguh kyrpad ïa me; to ai ngan shem sngewbha ha khmat jong me, ko syiem kynrad.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba u syiem Dabid u la poi haduh Bahurim, ha khmih, la mih nangta uwei u briew uba na ka kur ka ïing u Saul, uba kyrteng “u Shimei”, u khun u Gera: une te u la wan mih, u da tim ïaïaid.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la shat maw ïa u Dabid, bad ha ki shakri u syiem Dabid baroh; te u paidbah baroh bad kita kiba shynrang ïapom baroh ki la don sha kamon bad sha kadiang jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Shimei haba u tim u ong kumne, “Khie leit noh me, Khie leit noh me, u briew uba bit snam, me u briew u Belial:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Trai u la pynphai halor jong me ïa kata ka snam ka ïing u Saul baroh, uba me la synshar ma me ha ka jaka jong u; bad U Trai u la ai noh ïa ka hima ha ka kti u Absalom u khun jong me; bad ha khmih, me la ngat ha la ka jong ka pop, namar ba me long u briew uba bit snam.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ynda kumta, u Abishai u khun ka Seruïah u la ong ha u syiem, “Balei une u 'sew ïap u tim ïa u syiem kynrad jong nga? nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ïa nga ba ngan leit sha shiliang, ban khrai ïa ka khlieh jong u.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u syiem u la ong, “Ngan rat donkam aïu bad phi, phi ki khun u Seruïah? Namar ba u tim noh, bad namar U Trai u la ong ïa u, ‘To tim ïa u Dabid’; uei uba nud ong, ‘Balei me la leh kumne?’ ”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong ha u Abishai, bad ha la ki shakri baroh, “Ha khmih, u khun jong nga, uba la mih na ka kpoh jong nga, u wad ïa ka jingim jong nga: sa katno tam te kumta une u kynja Benjamin? To iehnoh ïa u, un wat tim; naba U Trai u la hukum ïa u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Lehse U Trai un khmih ïa kane ka pop ba la leh ha nga, bad un ai U Trai ïa nga da ka babha namar ka jingtim jong u ïa nga ha kane ka sngi.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te kumta, u Dabid bad u paidbah jong u ki nang ïaid ha lynti: u Shimei ruh u nang ïaid ha ka ranab lum ha marpyrshah jong u, bad katba u nang leit u nang tim artad, bad u la kawang maw ha u, bad u la pynmih pui pui.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u syiem, bad uta u paidbah baroh uba la don lem bad u, ki la thait; bad ki la shongthait hangta.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Absalom, bad u paidbah ki rangbah Israel baroh, ki la wan sha Jerusalem, bad u Ahithophel ryngkat bad u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te haba u Hushai u nong Arkhi, u lok u Dabid, u la wan ha u Absalom, u Hushai u la ong ha u Absalom, “To un im u syiem, to un im u syiem.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U Absalom te u la ong ïa u Hushai, “Dei kane pleng ka jinglehbha jong me ïa la u lok? balei ba mem shym leit lem bad la u lok?”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Hushai u la ïathuh ha u Absalom, “Em; hynrei, ïa uba un jied U Trai, bad une u paidbah, bad ki rangbah Israel baroh, ngan long u jong uta keiñ, bad lem bad uta ngan sah ruh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hato ïano pat ngan shakri? hato ngan ym shakri ha khmat u khun jong u? kumjuh kumba nga la shakri ha khmat u kpa jong me, kumta ngan long ha khmat jong me ruh.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ynda kumta, u Absalom u la ong ïa u Ahithophel, “To ïapyrkhat buit lang ïa kaba kumno ngin leh.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u Ahithophel u la ïathuh ha u Absalom, “To leit bsut ha kita ki tnga kliar jong u kpa jong me, ïa kiba u la pynsah ban sumar ïing; te ki Israel baroh kin ïohsngew ba u kpa jong me u la isaitmet ïa me: hangta yn pynkhlaiñ ïa ki kti jong kine baroh kiba ryngkat bad me.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumta, ki la pynïeng ïingjaiñ ïa u Absalom halor jrong ïing, bad u Absalom u la leit bsut sha kita ki tnga kliar u kpa jong u ha khmat ki Israel baroh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ka jingpynibuit u Ahithophel, kaba u ju pyni buit ha kita ki sngi, ka la long kumjuh kumba la ïakylli na ka ktien U Blei: kumta keiñ, ka la long ka jingpynibuit u Ahithophel baroh, ha u Dabid ruh bad ha u Absalom de."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Ahithophel u la ong ruh ha u Absalom, “To shah mynta ba ngan jied khat-ar hajar ki rangbah, bad ngan mih bad ngan beh nadien u Dabid ha kane hi ka miet:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> te ngan lap ïa u haba u dang thait bad ba u duna bor, bad ngan pynsheptieng ïa u: te kita ki briew baroh kiba ryngkat bad u kin phet ïap noh; bad ngan shoh pynïap tang ïa u syiem hi:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> kumta, ngan pynphai sha me ïa u paidbah baroh: uta u briew uba me wad ïa u, u long kumjuh kumba ki la phai pat baroh: kumta, u paidbah baroh un long ha kaba suk.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te kata ka jingong ka la idei shibun ha khmat u Absalom, bad ha khmat ki tymmen basan ki Israel baroh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ynda kumta, u Absalom u la ong, “Mynta to khot ïa u Hushai u nong Arkhi ruh, bad ngin sngap ruh ïa kaba un ong ma u.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba u Hushai u la wan ha u Absalom, u Absalom u la kren ha u, da kaba ong, “U Ahithophel u la kren kumne: kumno, ngin leh katba kum ka ktien jong u? Lada em, to kren sa ma me.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Hushai te u la ong ha u Absalom, “Ha kane shi sien kata ka buit kaba u la pyni u Ahithophel kam long ka babha.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Hushai u la ong ruh, “Me ithuh ïa la u kpa bad ïa ki rangbah jong u, ba ki long kiba shynrang ki briew, bad kiba bitar la ki jingmut, kum ka dngiem kaba la jah noh la ki khun ha khlaw: u kpa jong me u long u riewïapom ruh, te un ym sah miet ryngkat bad u paidbah.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ha khmih, u rieh ha kano kano ka krem, lane ha kano kano kawei pat ka jaka: bad haba kin kyllon katto katne na ki ha kaba sdang, te uno uno u ban ïohsngew ïa kata un ong keiñ, ‘Ka jingpynïap ka don hapdeng uta u paidbah uba bud ïa u Absalom.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hangta, wat uba shlur ruh, uba ka dohnud kum ka dohnud u sing, un jem noh jai: naba ki Israel baroh ki tip ba u kpa jong me u long uba shynrang ïapom, bad ba kita ki rangbah kiba bad u ki long kiba ïaw mynsiem.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, nga pyni buit ban lum khar paid ïa ki Israel baroh phar sha me, naduh Dan haduh Beer-sheba, u paidbah babun kat u shyiap uba harud ka duriaw; bad ba men leit ma me ruh da la ka met sha ka thma.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kumta, ngin lap ïa u ha kano kano ka jaka kat ha kaba yn shem ïa u, bad ngin tur ha u kumba hap ka umjer ha ka khyndew: te yn ym pynsah wat uwei ruh na u lymne na kita ki briew baroh kiba don lem bad u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Lada u la rung shapoh kawei ka nongbah ruh, hangta ki Israel baroh kin ïawallam ki tyllai sha kata ka shnong, bad ngin ïaring noh ïa ka sha ka wah, haduh ba yn ym shem hangta wat iwei i maw.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Absalom bad ki rangbah Israel baroh ki la ïa-ong, “Ban ïa ka jingpynibuit u Ahithophel lah ka jingpynibuit u Hushai u nong Arkhi.” Naba U Trai u la buh khnang ban pynduh noh ïa ka jingpynibuit ka babha u Ahithophel, khnang ba U Trai un ïoh pynwan ïa ka jingsniew halor u Absalom.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ynda kumta, u Hushai u la ong ha u Sadok bad ha u Abiathar ki lyngdoh, “Kumta kumta u Ahithophel u la pyni buit ha u Absalom bad ha ki tymmen basan ki Israel; bad kumta kumta nga ruh nga la pyni buit.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Mynta te, to phah kloi ban ïathuh ha u Dabid, da kaba ong, ‘Wat sah miet mynta ha ki khriang ka ri khlaw, hynrei, la kumno kumno khie leit sha shiliang; ba ïoh yn bam duh ïa u syiem, bad ïa uta u paidbah baroh uba don lem bad u.’ ”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Jonathan bad u Ahimaas ki dang ïa-ap hajan En-rogel; bad ka samla ka ju leit ïathuh ha ki; ki ruh ki la leit ïathuh ha u syiem Dabid; naba kim bit ban pynpaw ïa lade ban wan sha shnong.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hynrei, uwei u samla u la ïohi ïa ki, bad u la ïathuh ha u Absalom: te ki la leit noh kloi baroh ar ngut, bad ki la wan sha ïing uwei u briew ha Bahurim, uta te u la don ka pukri ha la ka phyllaw; bad ki la hiar sha kata.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad kata ka briew ka la shim ïa ka jingtap bad ka la siang halor kata ka pukri bad ka la thad ïa u Kew ba la tylliat halor kata; kumta ym shym tip ei ei.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad haba ki shakri u Absalom ki la wan sha kata ka briew ha kata ka ïing, ki la ïakylli, “U Ahimaas bad u Jonathan ki hangno?” Te kata ka briew ka la ïathuh ha ki, “Ki la leit sha shiliang kata ka wah duid.” Kumta, haba ki la wad ïa ki bad ba kim shem, ki la leit phai noh sha Jerusalem.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ynda kita ki la leit wan noh, kita kiwei ki la mih noh artet na kata ka pukri, bad ki la leit ïathuh ha u syiem Dabid; bad ki la ong ha u Dabid, “To ïeng, bad leit kloi sha shiliang kata ka um: naba kumne u Ahithophel u la shetbuit pyrshah ïa phi.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hangta u Dabid u la ïeng, bad uta u paidbah baroh uba don lem bad u, bad ki la leit sha shiliang ka Jordan: hamar ba ka la shai mynstep um shym sah uwei na ki u bym shym leit shiliang ka Jordan.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba u Ahithophel u la ïohi ba ym shym leh kumba u la pyni buit ma u, u la teh jin ha la ka kadda, bad u la ïeng, bad u la leit sha la ïing, ha ka shnong jong u, bad haba u la pynbeit ïa la ka ïing, u la phasi ïa lade; bad u la ïap, bad la tep ïa u ha u maw jingtep u kpa jong u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la leit sha Mahanaim. Bad u Absalom u la leit sha shiliang ka Jordan, ma u bad u paidbah Israel baroh lem bad u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Absalom u la thung ïa u Amasa halor u paidïapom ha ka jaka u Joab. Te une u Amasa u la long u khun jong uwei u briew, uba kyrteng “u Ithra” u kynja Israel, une u la leit bsut sha ka Abigail ka khun u Nahash, ka para ka Seruïah ka kmie u Joab.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kumta, ki Israel bad u Absalom ki la ïashong dara ha ka ri Gilead.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te haba u Dabid u la wan sha Mahanaim, u Shobi u khun u Nahash na Rabbah jong ki Ammon, bad u Makhir u khun u Ammiel na Lo-debar, bad u Barsillai u nong Gilead na Rogelim,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ki la ïawallam ki jingthiah, bad ki khuri, bad ki khiew khyndew, bad u Kew, bad u Kew Barli, bad u moida, bad u khaw shira, bad ki bin, bad u dai, bad u pyrthiew,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> bad ka ngap, bad ka makhon, bad ki langbrot, bad ka ktung dud masi, ha u Dabid bad ha uta u paidbah uba bad u, ba kin ïoh bam: naba ki la ong, “U paidbah u thngan bad u la thait, bad u sliang, ha kane ka ri khlaw.”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ñiew ïa u paidbah uba la don bad u, bad u la buh ki rangbah shihajar bad ki rangbah shispah halor jong ki.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Dabid u la phah lai bynta ïa u paidbah, shi bynta hapoh ka kti u Joab, bad shi bynta hapoh ka kti u Abishai u khun ka Seruïah, u para u Joab, bad shi bynta hapoh ka kti u Ittai u nong Gitt. Bad u syiem u la ong ïa u paidbah, “Shisha nga ruh ngan mih lem bad phi.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hynrei, u paidbah u la ïathuh, “Me men ym mih: namar lada ngin phet ïap, kin ym suidñiew ïa ngi; bad lada ngin ïap ma ngi marshiteng, kin ym suidñiew ïa ngi: hynrei, me, me long kum shiphew hajar na ngi: namar kata te, ka kham bha ïa me ban long ka jingïarap ïa ngi na kane ka shnong.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u syiem u la ong ha ki, “Ngan leh ïa kaba phi kham ibit ma phi.” Bad u syiem u la ïeng hajan ka khyrdop, bad u paidbah baroh u la leit mih noh shispah shispah bad shi hajar shi hajar.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u syiem u la hukum ïa u Joab bad ïa u Abishai bad ïa u Ittai, da kaba ong, “To leh jem na ka bynta jong nga ïa uta u khynnah, ïa u Absalom.” Bad u paidbah baroh u la ïohsngew haba u syiem u la ai hukum ïa ki kaptan baroh shaphang u Absalom.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta, u paidbah u la leit mih noh sha madan ban ïaleh ïa ki Israel: te kata ka thma ka la long ha ka khlaw Ephraim.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad hangta la pynïap ïa u paidbah Israel ha khmat ki shakri u Dabid, bad ka jingpynïap kaba khraw ka la don hangta ha kata ka sngi jin arphew hajar ngut.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Naba ka thma ka la saphred hangta halor ka khmat kata ka ri baroh: bad ka khlaw hi ka la bam duh kham bun ki briew ha kata ka sngi ban ïa kaba ka la bam duh ka waitlam.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Absalom, da kaba jia ryngkhat, u la ïashem bad ki shakri u Dabid. Bad u Absalom u la shong halor u khashor, te uta u khashor u la leit hapoh ki tnat kiba khah jong uwei u dieng Sning uba heh, bad u la sahkut ka khlieh ha uta u dieng Sning, kumta u la sdien hapdeng ka bneng bad ka khyndew; bad uta u khashor uba hapoh jong u, u la phet noh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te uwei u briew u la ïohi ïa kata, bad u la ïathuh ha u Joab, bad u la ong, “Ha khmih nga la ïohi ïa u Absalom ba la sdien ha u dieng Sning.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Joab u la ong ha uta u briew uba la ïathuh ha u, “Ha khmih, me la ïohi, te balei ba mem shym shoh ïa u hangta haduh ka khyndew? te ngan da la ai ïa me ka rupa shiphew shekel, bad ka jingpanpoh kawei.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te uta u briew u la ïathuh ha u Joab, “Lada nga ïoh ha la ka kti shi hajar shekel, ngan ym treh ban rah ïa la ka kti pyrshah ïa u khun u syiem: naba ha kaba ngi ïohsngew ma ngi u syiem u la hukum ïa me bad ïa u Abishai bad ïa u Ittai, u da ong, ‘To sumar mano mano ba un ym ktah ïa u khynnah u Absalom.’",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Lymda kumta, lada nga la leh mutlop pyrshah ïa ka jingim jong u, (bad ym don ei ei ba la buhrieh na u syiem,) bad ma me hi keiñ men da la iehnoh noh ïa nga.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hangta u Joab u la ong, “Nga ngam lah ïeng shuh kumne bad me.” Te u la shim lai tylli ki sum ha la ka kti, bad u sum ïa ki lyngba ïa ka dohnud u Absalom, haba u dang im hapdeng uta u dieng Sning.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad kita ki samla shiphew ngut kiba rah ïa ki atiar u Joab ki la ker sawdong bad ki la shoh ïa u Absalom, bad ki la pynïap ïa u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Joab u la put ïa ka ronsing, bad u paidbah u la wan phai noh na kaba beh nadien ki Israel: naba u Joab u la khang ïa u paidbah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ki la shim ïa u Absalom bad ki la bred ïa u sha ka thliew kaba khraw ha kata ka khlaw, bad halor jong u ki la buh maw shikynton kaba khraw eh: ki Israel baroh te ki la phet ïap uwei uwei sha la ka ïingjaiñ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Absalom mynba u dang im u la shim bad u la pynïeng uta u mawbynna ïa lade uba ha ka them u syiem: naba u la ong, “Ngam don khun shynrang u ban pynlong jingkynmaw ïa ka kyrteng jong nga”: bad u la kyrteng ïa uta u mawbynna ha la ka jong ka kyrteng. Te haduh kane ka sngi, ki khot ïa uta, “u Maw u Absalom”.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ynda kumta, u Ahimaas u khun u Sadok u la ong, “To shah ïa nga mynta ban phet ban lam ktien ha u syiem, ba U Trai u la pynhiar kput na ka bynta jong u halor ki nongshun jong u.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U Joab te u la ong ha u, “Me men ym long u nonglam-ktien ha kane ka sngi, hynrei, men lam ktien ha kawei pat ka sngi: hynrei, ha kane ka sngi men ym lam ktien, namar ba u la ïap u khun u syiem.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hangta u Joab u la ong ïa u Kushi, “To khie leit ïathuh ha u syiem ïa kiei kiei kiba me la ïohi.” Bad u Kushi u la dem ngon ïa u Joab, bad u la phet.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda kumta, u Ahimaas u khun u Sadok u la ong pat sa shi sien ha u Joab, “La kumno kumno ruh, nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ïa nga ruh ban phet hadien u Kushi.” U Joab te u la ïathuh, “Ïa ka ban lei men phet ma me, ko khun, haba mem ïohnong na kane ka jingbna?”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Hynrei la kumno kumno,” u la ong, “to ngan phet”: u ruh u la ong ha u, “To phet.” Kumta, u Ahimaas u la phet na ka lynti ka madan, bad u la palat ïa u Kushi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Dabid u la shong hapdeng kita ki ar tylli ki khyrdop: te u nongap u la leit kiew halor jrong kata ka khyrdop halor ka kynroh, bad u la khmied la ki khmat, bad u la khmih, bad ha khmih, u briew uba phet weibriew.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad uta u nongap u la pyrta, bad u la ïathuh ha u syiem. Te u syiem u la ong, “Lada u long marwei, u don ka ktien ha la ka shyntur.” Bad uta u la wan bran bran, bad u la poi hajan.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad uta u nongap u la ïohi ba u phet sa uwei pat u briew: bad uta u nongap u la pyrta ha u nongap jingkhang, bad u la ong, “Ha khmih, sa uwei pat u briew uba phet weibriew.” U syiem te u la ong, “Uta ruh u lam ktien.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad uta u nongap u la ong, “Nga imat ka jingphet jong une uba shuwa kum ka jingphet u Ahimaas u khun u Sadok.” Te u syiem u la ong, “Uta u briew u babha, bad u wanlam da ka ktien ka babha.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te u Ahimaas u la pyrta bad u la ong ha u syiem, “Khublei.” Bad u la dem ngon la ka khmat haduh khyndew ha khmat u syiem, bad u la ong, “Long ba la kyrkhu U Trai U Blei jong me, uba la aiti noh ïa kita ki briew kiba la rah ïa la ka kti pyrshah ïa u syiem kynrad jong nga.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u syiem u la kylli, “U khynnah u Absalom u la lait im ne em?” Bad u Ahimaas u la ïathuh, “Haba u Joab u la phah ïa u shakri u syiem, bad ïa nga u shakri jong me, nga la ïohi ïa ka jingkhihwin ka bakhraw, hynrei, ïa kaba kumno ngam shym tip.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u syiem u la ong, “To phai noh kyrpang, bad to ïeng shane.” Kumta, u la phai noh kyrpang, bad u la ïeng thik.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te, ha khmih, u la wan uta u Kushi; bad u Kushi u la ong, “Ka ktien ïa u syiem kynrad: naba U Trai ha kane ka sngi u la pynhiar kput na ka bynta jong me halor kita baroh kiba la ïeng ïaleh ïa me.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te u syiem u la kylli ïa u Kushi, “U khynnah u Absalom u lait im ne em?” Bad u Kushi u la ïathuh, “To ki nongshun u syiem kynrad jong nga, bad kita baroh kiba ïeng pyrshah ban pynsniew ïa me, to kin long kumba long uta u samla keiñ.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u syiem u la sngewsih shibun, bad u la leit kiew sha kata ka kamra halor ka khyrdop, bad u la ïam: bad katba u leit, u la ong kumne, “Ko khun jong nga Absalom, ko khun jong nga, ko khun jong nga Absalom! A ban da nga la ïap ma nga na ka bynta jong me, ko Absalom, ko khun jong nga, ko khun jong nga!”"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te la ïathuh ha u Joab, “Ha khmih u syiem u ïam bad u ïambriew ïa u Absalom.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad kata ka jingjop ka la kylla jingïam ha kata ka sngi ha u paidbah baroh: naba u paidbah ha kata ka sngi u la ïohsngew ba ong, “U syiem u la sngewsih namar la u khun.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad uta u paidbah ha kata ka sngi u la shu ïaid rieh shapoh shnong, kumjuh kumba ïaid rieh u paidbah haba lehrain ba ki la phet ïap ha ka thma.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, u syiem u la tap ïa la ka khmat, bad u syiem u la pyrta da ka ktien kaba jam, “Ko khun jong nga Absalom, ko Absalom, ko khun jong nga, ko khun jong nga!”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Joab u la wan bsut shapoh ïing ha u syiem, bad u la ong, “Ha kane ka sngi me la pynlehrain ïa ki khmat ki shakri jong me baroh, kiba ha kane ka sngi ki la pynim ïa ka jingim jong me, bad ïa ka jingim ki khun shynrang bad ka jong ki khun kynthei jong me, bad ïa ka jingim ki tnga jong me, bad ïa ka jingim ki tnga kliar jong me;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ha kaba me ieit ïa la ki nongshun, bad ba me shun ïa la ki lok. Naba me la pyni ha kane ka sngi, ba mem ñiew ei ei ïa ki nongïalam lymne ïa ki shakri: naba nga, nga sngewthuh mynta, ba lada u la im u Absalom, bad ba ngi, ngi la ïap baroh ha kane ka sngi, me la sngewbha eh pynban.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Namar kata te, to ïeng, bad to mih shabar, bad to kren sngewbha ha la ki shakri: naba nga smai ha U Trai, ba lada men ym mih shabar, uwei ruh un ym sah bad me ha kane ka miet: bad kata kan kham sniew ïa me ban ïa ka jingsniew baroh kaba la jia ïa me naduh ba me dang samla haduh mynta.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem u la ïeng, bad u la shong ha kata ka khyrdop. Te la pynbna ha u paidbah baroh, da kaba ong, “Ha khmih, u syiem u shong ha ka khyrdop”: bad u paidbah baroh u la wan ha khmat u syiem. Te ki Israel ki la phet uwei uwei baroh sha la ka ïingjaiñ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki paidbah baroh ki la ïa-pyneh bad ki jaid Israel baroh, ki ïa-ong, “U syiem u la pyllait ïa ngi na ka kti ki nongshun jong ngi, bad u la pynim ïa ngi na ka kti ki Philistia; mynta te, u la phet na ka ri na u Absalom.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad une u Absalom, ïa uba ngi la pynsleh ban long halor jong ngi, u la ïap ha ka thma. Namar kata te, balei phim ïakren shaphang ka ban wallam pat ïa u syiem?”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u syiem Dabid u la phah ha ki lyngdoh u Sadok bad u Abiathar, u da ong, “To kren ha ki tymmen basan ki Judah, da kaba ong, ‘Kumno phi, phi ïalong khatduh ban wallam pat ïa u syiem sha la ïing, haba ka jingkren ki Israel baroh ka la poi sha u syiem, ban wallam pat ïa u syiem sha la ïing?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Phi long ki para jong nga, phi ka shyieng jong nga bad ka doh jong nga: namar kata te, kumno phi long ki bakhatduh ïa ka ban wallam pat ïa u syiem?’",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> To ong ha u Amasa ruh, ‘Me mem long ka shyieng jong nga bad ka doh jong nga? U Blei un leh kumne ïa nga, bad un pyntam ruh, lada me men ym long kaptan u paidïapom ha khmat jong nga ha la ka sngi ha ka jaka u Joab.’ ”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u la pyndem ïa ka dohnud ki rangbah Judah baroh, kumjuh kum ïa ka jong uwei u briew; kumta, ki la phah ktien sha u syiem, ki da ong, “To wan phai ma me bad ki shakri jong me baroh.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kumta, u syiem u la leit phai noh, bad u la wan sha Jordan. Bad ki Judah ki la wan sha Gilgal ïa ka ban leit tan ïa u syiem, ïa ka ban wallam ïa u syiem halor ka Jordan.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Shimei u khun u Gera, u nong Benjamin, uba na Bahurim, u la pynkloi bad u la wan hiar lem bad ki rangbah Judah ïa ka ban tan ïa u syiem Dabid.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki la don lem bad u shi hajar ki rangbah Benjamin, bad u Siba ruh uta u shakri ka ïing u Saul, bad la ki khun shynrang khatsan ngut bad la ki shakri arphew ngut lem bad u; bad ki la leit sha shiliang ka Jordan ha khmat u syiem.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad la pynleit ïa ka lieng khawa sha shiliang ïa ka ban wallam ïa ki ba-ha-ïing u syiem, bad ïa ka ban leh ei ei katba u ibit ma u. Bad u Shimei u khun u Gera u la hap dem ha khmat u syiem, haba u la dang ryngkang ïa ka Jordan.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u la ong ha u syiem, “To u kynrad jong nga wat ai ba un pynkit pop halor jong nga, lymne wat kynmaw ïa kata kaba u shakri jong me u la leh bymman ha kata ka sngi ba u syiem kynrad jong nga u la leit noh na Jerusalem, ba u syiem un buhnud ïa kata.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Naba nga u shakri jong me nga tip ba nga la leh pop: namar kata, ha khmih, ha kane ka sngi nga la wan nyngkong eh na ka ïing u Joseph baroh ïa ka ban hiar ban wan tan ïa u syiem kynrad jong nga.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, u Abishai u khun ka Seruïah u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Namar kane pleng yn ym pynïap ïa u Shimei, haba u la tim ïa uba la sleh jong U Trai?”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Dabid u la ïathuh, “Nga donkam aïu bad phi, phi ki khun ka Seruïah, ba phin long ki nongïaleh pyrshah ïa nga ha kane ka sngi? hato yn pynïap ïa uno uno ha Israel ha kane ka sngi? namar nga tip ne em ba ha kane ka sngi nga long u syiem halor ki Israel?”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u syiem u la ong ha u Shimei, “Men ym ïap.” Bad u syiem u la smai ha u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Mephibosheth u khun u Saul ruh u la wan hiar ban tan ïa u syiem; te um shym la sum ïa la ki kjat, lymne shna ïa la ki tmain, lymne sait ïa la ki jaiñ, naduh kata ka sngi ba u la leit noh u syiem haduh ka sngi ba u la wan sha la ïing ha kaba suk.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te haba u la wan sha Jerusalem ban ïashem bad u syiem, u syiem u la ong ïa u, “Ko Mephibosheth, me balei mem shym la leit lem bad nga?”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U te u la ïathuh, “Ko syiem kynrad, u shakri jong nga u la shukor ïa nga: naba u shakri jong me u la ong, ‘Ngan sa teh jin ïa ka kadda, ba ngan shong halor jong ka, ba ngan dup leit bad u syiem,’ naba u shakri jong me u ba-dkoh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u la kren siar sniew ïa la u shakri ha u syiem kynrad jong nga; hynrei, u syiem kynrad jong nga u long kum u angel U Blei: namar kata, to leh ïa kaba ibit ha khmat jong me.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Naba ka ïing u kpa jong nga baroh ki la long tang ki riewïap ha khmat u syiem kynrad jong nga: pynban, me la buh ïa la u shakri hapdeng kita kiba bam ha ka miej jong me hi. Namar kata, nga dang don ka hok aïu ba ngan nang lynñiar shuh ha u syiem?”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u syiem u la ong ha u, “Ïa ka ban lei me shu dang kren ïa la ki kam? Nga ong, ‘Ma me bad u Siba phin ïabynta ïa kata ka khyndew.’ ”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te u Mephibosheth u la ong ha u syiem, “Ho-oid keiñ, to un shim ma u ïa kiei kiei baroh, haba u syiem kynrad jong nga u la wan pat sha la ïing ha kaba suk.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u Barsillai u nong Gilead u la wan hiar na Rogelim; bad u la leit sha shiliang ka Jordan ryngkat bad u syiem, ïa ka ban leit on ïa u sha shiliang ka Jordan.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te u Barsillai u la tymmen eh, jin phraphew snem ka rta: bad u la long ma u uba la ai jingbam ïa u syiem mynba u la don ha Mahanaim; naba u la long u rangbah u bakhraw.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u syiem u la ong ha u Barsillai, “Ale sha shiliang bad nga, bad ngan bsa ïa me bad nga ha Jerusalem.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te u Barsillai u la ïathuh ha u syiem, “Nga dang sah sa katno snem pat ïa ka ban im, ba ngan leit kiew bad u syiem sha Jerusalem?",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ha kane ka sngi nga la phraphew snem ka rta: hato nga lah ban pynpher ïa ka babha bad ka basniew? Hato u shakri jong me u lah ban mad ïa kaba nga bam lane ïa kaba nga dih? Nga dang lah shuh mo ban ïohsngew ïa ka jingsawa ki nongrwai shynrang bad kynthei? Namar kata, u shakri jong me un lei un long pat ka jingkit ha u syiem kynrad jong nga?",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> U shakri jong me un shu leit bad u syiem khyndiat ha lyndet ka Jordan: te balei u syiem un siew pat ïa nga da ka jingai sngewbha kaba katne katne?",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ïa la u shakri ba un phai pat, ba ngan ïoh ïap ha la ka jong ka shnong, bad ba yn tep ïa nga hajan ka jingtep u kpa bad ka kmie jong nga. Hynrei, ha khmih, u Shimham, u shakri jong me; u te un leit sha shiliang bad u syiem kynrad jong nga; bad to leh ha u katba me ibit.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te u syiem u la ong, “U Shimham te un leit sha shiliang bad nga, bad ngan leh ha u ïa kaba me ibit: bad ïa kano kano kaba men buh halor jong nga, ïa kata ngan leh na ka bynta jong me.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad u paidbah baroh u la leit sha shiliang ka Jordan, u syiem ruh u la leit sha shiliang: bad u syiem u la doh ïa U Barsillai, bad u la kyrkhu ïa u; te u la leit wan noh sha la ka jong ka jaka.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Kumta, u syiem u la leit shiliang sha Gilgal, bad u Shimham u la leit shiliang lem bad u: bad u paidbah Judah baroh ki la wallam sha shiliang ïa u syiem, bad shiteng u paidbah Israel ruh.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te ha khmih, ki rangbah Israel baroh ki la wan sha u syiem, bad ki la ong ha u syiem, “Balei ba ki para jong ngi ki rangbah Judah ki la tuh ïa me, bad ki la wallam sha shiliang ka Jordan ïa u syiem, bad ïa ki ba-ha-ïing jong u, bad ïa ki rangbah u Dabid baroh lem bad u?”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te ki rangbah Judah baroh ki la ïathuh ha ki rangbah Israel, “Namar ba u syiem u ïadei kur jan ïa ngi; na ka balei te phi ïabitar namar kane ka kam? hato ngi la ïabam ei ei na ka jinglut u syiem? lane u la ai ka jingai ei ei ha ngi?”",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Bad ki rangbah Israel ki la ïathuh ha ki rangbah Judah, bad ki la ong, “Ngi, ngi don shiphew bynta ha u syiem, bad ngi don kham bun ruh ha u Dabid ban ïa phi: balei phi la ibeiñ te ïa ngi, ba ym shym la ïoh shuwa ïa ka jingpyrkhat jong ngi ha kaba wallam noh pat ïa u syiem jong ngi?” Te ki ktien ki rangbah Judah ki la kham eh ban ïa ki ktien ki rangbah Israel."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te la jia ba la don hangta u briew u Belial uba kyrteng “u Sheba”, u khun u Bikhri, u kynja Benjamin: une te u la put ïa ka ronsing, bad u la ong, “Ngi ngim don ka bynta ha u Dabid, lymne ngim don ka bynta ba hap ha u khun u Jesse: to uwei uwei baroh sha la ki ïingjaiñ, ko Israel.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kumta, ki rangbah Israel baroh ki la leit kiew noh na kaba bud ïa u Dabid, bad ki la bud ïa u Sheba u khun u Bikhri: hynrei, ki rangbah Judah ki la snoh ha la u syiem, naduh ka Jordan jin haduh Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Dabid u la wan sha la ïing ha Jerusalem; te u syiem u la shim ïa kita ki shiphew ngut ki kynthei, ki tnga kliar jong u, kiba u la lah pynsah ban sumar ïa ka ïing, bad u la buh ïa ki hapoh ka jingsumar, bad u la bsa ïa ki, hynrei, um shym bsut shuh sha ki. Kumta, la set khop ïa ki haduh ka sngi ka jingïap jong ki, ki da shong ha ka jinglong riewkynthei.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem u la ong ha u Amasa, “To khot lang sha nga ïa ki rangbah Judah hamar ka sngi ka balai, to don ma me ruh hangne.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumta u Amasa u la leit khot lang ïa ki Judah: hynrei, u la tud kham slem ïa kata ka por ba u la buh ha u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Abishai, “Une u Sheba u khun u Bikhri un kham pynsniew ïa ngi ban ïa kaba u la leh u Absalom: to shim ma me ïa ki shakri u kynrad jong me, bad to beh nadien jong u, ïoh ba un ïoh ïa ki shnong ba la ker kynroh, bad un lait noh na ngi.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ki la leit mih hadien jong u ki rangbah u Joab, bad ki Khereth bad ki Peleth, bad ki rangbah badonbor baroh: bad ki la leit mih noh na Jerusalem, ïa ka ban beh nadien u Sheba u khun u Bikhri.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Haba ki la don ha u mawbah uba ha Gibeon, u Amasa u la wan tan ïa ki. Te u Joab u la panpoh da kata ka jaiñkup hiar thma jong u ïa kaba u la phong, bad ha kata la don ka jingpanpoh kaba bad ka waitlam ha ka jingsop jong ka, ba la teh ha ka syngkai jong u; te katba u ïaid kata ka hap noh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Joab u la ong ha u Amasa, “Kumno, me bha, ko para?” Bad u Joab u la bat ïa u Amasa da ka kti kamon na u 'ñiuh tmoh ïa ka ban doh ïa u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, u Amasa um shym khmih ïa kata ka waitlam ha ka kti u Joab: kumta u la dung ïa u da ka na ka kpoh, bad u la pynmih noh ïa ki snier jong u ha ka khyndew, bad um shym shoh pat ïa u; bad u la ïap. Te u Joab bad u Abishai u para jong u ki la beh nadien u Sheba u khun u Bikhri.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad uwei na ki shakri u Joab u ïeng hajan jong u, bad u la ong, “Kat uba imon ïa u Joab, bad kat uba ha ka liang u Dabid, to un bud ïa u Joab.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Amasa u la ksaid ha la ka snam hapdeng ka lynti bah. Te haba uta u briew u la ïohi ba u paidbah baroh u shu ïeng, u la rah noh ïa u Amasa na ka lynti bah sha lyngkha, bad u la tap jaiñ halor jong u, haba u la ïohi ba uwei uwei baroh uba wan hajan jong u, u shu ïeng.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Haba la pynkynriah noh ïa u na kata ka lynti bah, ki rangbah baroh ki la leit bud ïa u Joab, ïa ka ban beh nadien u Sheba u khun u Bikhri.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u la leit lyngba ïa ki jaid Israel baroh haduh Abel, bad haduh Beth-maakhah, bad ki Berit baroh: bad ki la lum lang, bad ki la bud ïa u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kumta, ki la wan bad ki la ker kut ïa u ha Abel-beth-maakah, bad ki la kynton ïa ka kynroh lyngstong pyrshah ïa kata ka shnong, bad ka la ïeng marpyrshah ïa ka kynroh ker: te kita ki briew baroh kiba la don bad u Joab ki la krang ïa ka kynroh, ïa ka ban pynkyllon ïa ka.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hangta kawei ka kynthei ka bastad kaba na kata ka shnong ka la pyrta, “Ha sngap, ha sngap; nga kyrpad ïa phi, to ong ha u Joab, ‘Ale shane hajan, ba ngan ïoh ïakren bad me.’ ”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u la wan hajan sha ka; bad kata ka kynthei ka la kylli, “Long ma me u Joab?” U te u la ong, “Nga long.” Hangta ka la ong ha u, “To sngap ïa ki ktien ka shakri jong me.” U ruh u la ïathuh, “Nga ïohsngew.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ka la kren, ka da ong, “Ki la ju kren mynhyndai, ki ïa-ong, ‘Shisha kin ïawad buit ha Abel’: te kumta ki la keiñ noh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Nga, nga long na kita kiba ïasuk bad kiba ïaineh ha Israel: me pyrshang ban pynjot noh ïa ka nongbah bad ïa ka kmie ha Israel: men pynduh balei ïa ka bynta ka jong U Trai?”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Joab u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Kam kumta, kam kumta, em, ba ngan pynjot lane pynduh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ka kam, kam long kumta: hynrei, u briew uba na ka ri lum Ephraim, u Sheba u khun u Bikhri da ka kyrteng, u la rah la ka kti pyrshah ïa u syiem, pyrshah ïa u Dabid keiñ: to aiti noh tang ïa uta, te ngan leit noh na kane ka nongbah.” Te kata ka kynthei ka la ong ha u Joab, “Ha khmih, ïa ka khlieh jong u yn bred noh ha me nalor ka kynroh.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te kata ka kynthei ka la leit da la ka jingstad ha ki rangbah baroh. Bad ki la khrai khlieh ïa u Sheba u khun u Bikhri, bad ki la bred noh shabar ha u Joab. U te u la put ïa ka ronsing, bad ki la saphred na kata ka nongbah, uwei uwei baroh sha la ka ïingjaiñ. Bad u Joab u la leit wan noh sha Jerusalem ha u syiem.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te u Joab u la long halor ki paidïapom ki Israel baroh: bad u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada u la long halor ki Khereth bad halor ki Peleth:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad u Adoram u la long halor ka khajna: bad u Jehoshaphat u khun u Ahilud u nongthoh rekord:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> bad u Sheba u la long u nongthoh; bad u Sadok bad u Abiathar ki long lyngdoh:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad u Ira ruh u kynja Jair u la long u lyngdoh ha u Dabid."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te la don ha ki sngi u Dabid ka 'nemsniew lai snem lynter; bad u Dabid u la wad ïa ka khmat U Trai. Bad U Trai u la ong, “Ka long namar u Saul, bad namar ka ïing kaba bit snam jong u, namar ba u la pynïap ïa ki Gibeon.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u syiem u la khot ïa ki Gibeon, bad u la ong ha ki; (te kita ki Gibeon kim shym long na ki khun Israel, hynrei, na kita kiba sah na ki Amor; bad ki khun Israel ki la smai ha ki: u Saul te u la pyrshang ban pynïap ïa ki ha ka jingshitrhem na ka bynta ki khun Israel bad Judah:)",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad u Dabid u la ong ha ki Gibeon, “Ngan leh aïu na ka bynta jong phi? bad da ei ngan pynlong ka kuna, ba phin dup kyrkhu ïa ka jingïoh kynti ka jong U Trai?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ki Gibeon te ki la ong ha u, “Ka kam jong ngi bad u Saul, lane ka ïing jong u, kam long ka jong ka rupa lane ka ksiar; lymne kam dei ïa ngi ban pynïap ïa uno uno u briew ha Israel.” Bad u la ong, “Ïa kaba phin ong, ïa kata ngan leh na ka bynta jong phi.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ki te ki la ong ha u syiem, “Uta u briew uba la bam duh ïa ngi, bad uba ïashet pyrshah ïa ngi, ba yn pynjot ïa ngi ba ngin ym sah ha kino kino ki phang ka ri Israel,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> to aiti hynñiew ngut ki rangbah na ki khun jong u ha ngi, te ngin phasi ïa ki ha U Trai ha Gibeah u Saul, uba la jied jong U Trai.” Bad u syiem u la ong, “Ngan aiti ïa ki.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, u syiem u la pynim ïa u Mephibosheth, u khun u Jonathan u khun u Saul, namar kata ka jingïakular U Trai kaba la don hapdeng jong ki, hapdeng u Dabid keiñ bad u Jonathan u khun u Saul.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, u syiem u la shim ar ngut ki khun ka Rispah ka khun u Aïah, ïa kiba ka la kha ha u Saul, u Armoni bad u Mephibosheth; bad san ngut ki khun ka Mikhal ka khun u Saul, ïa kiba ka la kha ha u Adriel u khun u Barsillai u kynja Meholath:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad u la ai noh ïa ki ha ki kti ki Gibeon, ki ruh ki la phasi ïa ki ha uta u lum ha khmat U Trai, bad ki la ïakyllon lang baroh hynñiew ngut: te la pynïap ïa ki ha ki sngi ka aïom ot, ha ki sngi ki banyngkong ha kaba sdang ka aïom ot u Kew Barli.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ka Rispah ka khun u Aïah ka la shim da ka jaiñ khain, bad ka la siang ïa ka ïa lade ha uta u mawsiang, naduh kaba sdang ka aïom ot haduh ba ka um ka la hiar halor jong ki na bneng; bad kam shym shah lymne ïa ki sim bneng ban sah ha ki mynsngi, lymne ïa ki mrad khlaw mynmiet.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te la ïathuh ha u Dabid ïa kaba ka la leh ka Rispah ka khun u Aïah, ka tnga kliar ka jong u Saul.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Dabid u la leit shim ïa ki shyieng jong u Saul bad ki shyieng jong u Jonathan u khun jong u na ki rangbah Jabesh-gilead, kiba la lah tuh ïa ki na ka lynti bah ka Beth-shan, ha kaba ki Philistia ki la phasi ïa ki, ha kata ka sngi ba ki Philistia ki la pynïap ïa u Saul ha Gilboa:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad u la wallam artet nangta ïa ki shyieng jong u Saul bad ki shyieng jong u Jonathan u khun jong u; bad ki la lum ruh ïa ki shyieng jong kita ïa kiba la phasi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ki la tep ïa kita ki shyieng jong u Saul bad ki jong u Jonathan u khun jong u ha ka ri Benjamin ha Sela ha u maw jingtep u Kish u kpa jong u: bad ki la pyndep ïa kiei kiei baroh ba u la hukum u syiem. Hadien kata te, U Blei u la sngewbha ïa ka ri.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ka thma ka la long pat hapdeng ki Philistia bad ki Israel; bad u Dabid u la leit hiar lem bad ki shakri jong u ruh, bad u la ïaleh thma ïa ki Philistia: u Dabid te u la thait ïan.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Ishbi-benob, uba la long na ki khun u radbah, uba ka jingkhia u sum jong u ka la long laispah shekel ka rnong, bad haba u la panpoh da ka waitlam ka bathymmai, u la mut ban pynïap ïa u Dabid.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, u Abishai u khun ka Seruïah u la ïarap ïa u, bad u la shoh ïa u Philistia, bad u la pynïap ïa u. Namar kata, ki rangbah u Dabid ki la smai ha u, ki da ong, “Men ym ïoh mih shabar shuh bad ngi sha ka thma, ïoh ba men pynlip ïa ka sharak jong ki Israel.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hadien kata, ka la long pat ka thma bad ki Philistia ha Gob: hangta, u Sibbekai u kynja Hushath u la pynïap ïa u Saph, uba la long na ki khun u radbah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hadien kata, ka la long thma pat bad ki Philistia ha Gob; bad u Elhanan u khun u Jaare-oregim u nong Bethlehem u la pynïap ïa u Goliath u nong Gitt, uba u dieng sum jong u, u la long kat u khung jong u nongthain jaiñ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te la don thma pat ha Gath, ha kaba la don u briew uba heh met, uba la don hynriew tylli ki shynriah'ti ha kawei kawei ka kti, bad hynriew tylli ki shynriah'jat ha kawei kawei ka kjat, arphew saw tylli ha ka jingkheiñ; bad une ruh u la long u khun jong uta u radbah.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te haba u la beiñ ïa ki Israel, u Jonathan u khun u Shimei uba u para u Dabid u la pynïap ïa u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ïa kine saw ngut la kha ha uta u radbah ha Gath; bad ki la kyllon da ka kti u Dabid, bad da ka kti ki shakri jong u."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Dabid u la kren ïa ki ktien jong kane ka jingrwai ha U Trai ha kata ka sngi ba U Trai u la pyllait ïa u na ka kti ki nongshun jong u baroh, bad na ka kti u Saul:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad u la ong, “U Trai u long u mawsiang jong nga, bad ka kut jong nga, bad u nongpynim jong nga, u jong nga keiñ;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Blei uba u mawsiang jong nga, ha u keiñ ngan shaniah; ka stieh jong nga, bad ka reng ka jingpynim jong nga, ka kut bajrong jong nga, bad ka jaka rieh jong nga; u nongpynim jong nga, me pynim ïa nga na ka jingleh-jubor.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ngan khot kyrpad ïa U Trai, uba dei ban ïoh ïaroh; kumta yn pynim ïa nga na ki nongshun jong nga.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Naba ki jingat phyllung ka jingïap ki la ker tawiar ïa nga, ki jingshlei ka jingbymman ki la pynsheptieng ïa nga.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ki jingkhum ka dujok ki la ker sawdong ïa nga; ki jingriam ka jingïap ki la lap ïa nga.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Ha la ka jingjynjar nga la khot kyrpad ha U Trai, nga la kyrpad jam ruh ïa U Blei: bad u la ïohsngew ïa ka jingsawa jong nga na ka templ jong u, bad ka jinglynñiar jong nga ka la poi sha ki shkor jong u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Hangta ka pyrthei ka la khih bad ka la khynñiuh, ïa ki nongrim jong ka bneng la pynkhih bad la pynkhynñiuh, namar ba u la bitar.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ka tdem ka la kiew na ki thliew khmut jong u, bad ka ding na ka shyntur jong u ka la bam duh: da ka, ka 'dewïong ka la meh ding.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U la pyndem ïa ki bneng ruh, bad u la wan hiar; bad ka jingdum tliw tliw ka la long hapoh ki sla'jat jong u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U la shong halor u Kherub, bad u la her: shisha, la ïohi ïa u halor ki thapniang ka lyer.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ïa ka jingdum u la pynlong ki ïingjaiñ baroh sawdong ïa u, ka jingïalang ki um keiñ, ki lyoh barben ka suiñ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na kata ka jingtyngshaiñ ka khmat jong u, ki rnga 'dewïong ki la meh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Trai u la riew pyrthat na bneng, bad uta U Bahakhlieh Tam u la pynjam ïa la ka ktien.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u la pynmih ïa ki khnam, bad u la pynsaphred ïa ki; ïa ki leilieh, bad u la pynphet krad ïa ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ki trai jong ka duriaw ki la paw, ïa ki nongrim jong ka pyrthei la pynlyngkhuit, da ka jingsneng ka jong U Trai, da kaba beh ka jingpyrsad ki thliew khmut jong u keiñ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “U la phah na sha jrong, bad u la shim noh ïa nga; u la pynmih noh ïa nga na ki babun ki um.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U la pynim ïa nga na u nongshun bakhrawbor jong nga, na kita kiba la shun ïa nga; namar ki la kham khlaiñ ïa nga.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki la lap ïa nga ha ka sngi ka jingjynjar jong nga: hynrei, U Trai u la long ka jingkyrshan ïa nga.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U la ïalam ïa nga sha ka jingkylluid ruh: u la pynim ïa nga, namar ba u la sngewieit ïa nga.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “U Trai u la ai nong ïa nga katba kum ka jinglehhok jong nga: katba kum ka jingkhuid ki kti jong nga u la siew ïa nga.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Naba nga la rakhe ïa ki lynti U Trai, bad ngam shym kiar leh bymman na U Blei jong nga.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Naba ki jingbishar jong u baroh ki la don ha khmat jong nga: bad na ki hukum jong u ngam shym la kiar.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Nga la long janai ruh ha khmat jong u, bad nga la sumar ïa lade na ka jingbymman jong nga.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Namar kata, U Trai u la ai nong ïa nga katba kum ka jinglehhok jong nga; katba kum ka jingkhuid jong nga ha ka jingikhmat jong u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Ïa uba isynei men leh isynei, ïa u briew u bajanai men leh janai;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ïa u bakhuid men leh khuid; bad ïa uba mutlop men leh mutlop.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ïa kita ki briew ki bajynjar men pynim: hynrei, ki khmat jong me ki ha kita kiba sngewmeng, ïa ka ban pynpoh ïa ki.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Naba me long ka sharak jong nga, A Trai: bad U Trai un pynshai ïa ka jingdum jong nga.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Naba da me nga tur lyngba ïa ka shi kynhun; da U Blei jong nga, nga rynsied halor ka kynroh.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> U Blei uba janai la ka lynti; ïa ka ktien jong U Trai la pynphrang; u long ka stieh ha kita baroh kiba shaniah ha u.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “Naba uei uba long U Blei, hynrei, tang U Trai? bad uei uba long u mawsiang, hynrei, tang U Blei jong ngi?",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> U Blei u long ka kut baskhem jong nga: bad u ïalam ïa uba janai ha ka lynti jong u.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> U pynlong ïa ki kjat jong nga kum ki jong ki skei: bad u buh ïa nga ha ki jaka kiba jrong jong nga.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> U hikai ma u ïa ki kti jong nga ban ïaleh thma; ba kumta, ki ksang'ti jong nga ki wiat ïa ka ryntieh rnong.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Me la ai ruh ha nga ïa ka stieh ka jingpynim jong me: bad ka jingjemnud jong me ka la pynkhraw ïa nga.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Me la pynkylluid ïa ki jingjam jong nga hapoh jong nga, te ki kjat jong nga kim shym la syntuid.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Nga la beh nadien ki nongshun jong nga, bad nga la pynjot ïa ki; te ngam shym wan phai noh tad ynda la bam duh noh ïa ki.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Nga la bam duh noh ïa ki, bad nga la sum lyngba ïa ki, ba kim lah shuh ban ïeng; ki la kyllon ruh hapoh ki sla'jat jong nga.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Naba me, me la pynpanpoh ïa nga da ka bor ïa ka thma: ïa kita kiba ïeng ïaleh ïa nga, me la pyndem hapoh jong nga.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Me la pynphai ruh ha nga ïa ki ingdong ki nongshun jong nga, ba kumta nga lah ban ot noh ïa kita kiba shun ïa nga.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ki la khmih, hynrei, ym don u ban pynim; ïa U Trai keiñ, hynrei, um shym phai ktien ïa ki.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Hangta nga la pynlwet jin ïa ki kum ka 'dewmet ka khyndew, nga la ïuh roit ïa ki kum ka ktieh ka lynti bah, bad nga pynsaphred kylleng ïa ki.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> “Me la pyllait ruh ïa nga na ki jingïania u paidbah jong nga; me la ïai-ri ïa nga ban long ha khlieh ki jaid bynriew: ki briew kiba ngam shym la ithuh ruh, kin shakri ïa nga.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Kita ki nongwei kin nguh ïa nga: ki tang shu ïohsngew shaphang jong nga, kin kohnguh ïa nga.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ki nongwei kin dam noh, bad kin mih da kaba khynñiuh, na kita ki jaka bakhim jong ki.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> “U Trai u im; bad to long ba la kyrkhu ïa u mawsiang jong nga; bad to ai ba yn pynkyntiew ïa U Blei u mawsiang ka jingpynim jong nga:",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> uta U Blei keiñ uba pynhiar kput na ka bynta jong nga, bad uba pynhapoh ïa ki jaid bynriew hapoh jong nga,",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> bad uba ïalam ïa nga na ki nongshun jong nga: me pynkyntiew ruh ïa nga halor kita kiba ïeng ïaleh ïa nga: me pyllait ïa nga na uta u briew uba leh jubor.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> “Namar kata, ngan ainguh ïa me, A Trai, hapdeng ki jaid bynriew, bad ngan rwai ïaroh ïa ka kyrteng jong me.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Ïa ka jingpynim kaba khraw u ai ha u syiem jong u: bad u leh isynei ïa uta uba la sleh jong u, ïa u Dabid keiñ, bad ïa u symbai jong u junom.”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te kine ki long ki ktien ki bakhatduh ki jong u Dabid. U Dabid u khun u Jesse u ong, bad uta u briew ïa uba la kyntiew sha jrong u ong, uta uba la sleh jong U Blei u Jakob, bad u nongrwai babang jong u Israel:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “U Mynsiem U Trai u la kren da nga, bad ka ktien jong u ka la long ha u thylliej jong nga.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Blei u Israel u la ong, U Mawsiang u Israel u la kren ha nga: ‘Uta uba synshar ïa ki briew da ka hok, uba synshar ha ka jingsheptieng ïa U Blei,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> uta un long kum ka jingshai mynstep, haba ka sngi ka dang mih, ka step ka bymdon lyoh; mynba u phlang ba dang lung u mih na khyndew, da ka jingtyngshaiñ basngur hadien u slap.’",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Shisha ka ïing jong nga kam long kumta bad U Blei, pynban, u la pynlong ka jutang kaba junom bad nga, ba la buh pynbeit ha kiei kiei baroh, bad kaba skhem: namar ba ka long ka jingpynim jong nga baroh, bad ka jingkwah jong nga baroh, la um pynman ïa ka.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, ki bymman baroh kin long kum ki dieng shiah ïa ki ban shu bred noh, namar ym lah ban shim ïa ki da ka kti:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> hynrei, uta u briew uba ktah ïa ki u dei ban rah ïa u nar bad u dieng jong u sum; bad yn thang duh ïa ki da ka ding ha la ka jaka.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kine ki kyrteng jong kita ki rangbah kiba don bor kiba u Dabid u la don: u Josheb-basshebeth jaid Tahkhemon, u rangbah jong ki kaptan; u la long uta u Adino u nong Esni, u la ïaleh ïa phraspah ngut ïa kiba la pynïap ha kajuh ka por.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te uba bud ha u, u la long u Eleasar u khun u Dodo u khun u kynja Ahohi, uwei na ki lai ngut ki rangbah badonbor kiba bad u Dabid, mynba ki la beiñ ïa kita ki Philistia kiba la lum lang ïa ka thma, bad ba ki rangbah Israel ki la leit noh:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> u la ïeng, bad u la shoh ïa ki Philistia, haduh ba la thait ka kti jong u, bad ka kti jong u ka la dait skhem ha ka waitlam: te U Trai u la pynlong ïa ka jingjop kaba khraw ha kata ka sngi; bad u paidbah u leit phai hadien jong u tang ban shu lute.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te uba bud ha uta u la long u Shammah u khun u Age u kynja Harar. Te ki Philistia ki la lum lang u paidbah paidsan, ha kaba la don ka lyngkha kaba dap da u dai; bad u paidbah u la phet ïap noh na ki Philistia.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, u la ïeng hapdeng kata ka lyngkha, bad u la da ïa ka, bad u la pynïap ïa ki Philistia: bad U Trai u la pynlong ïa ka jingjop kaba khraw.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad lai ngut na kita ki laiphew ngut ki rangbah ki la leit hiar, bad ki la wan ha u Dabid ha ka aïom ot sha kata ka krem Adullam; bad u paid jong ki Philistia u la shong dara ha ka them Rephaim.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te mynkata, u Dabid u la don ha ka kut, bad ka karod ki Philistia ka la don mynkata ha Bethlehem.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Dabid u la thrang, bad u la ong, “A ban da uno uno un ai um ïa nga ban dih na ka pukri Bethlehem, kaba hajan ka khyrdop?”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te kita ki lai ngut ki rangbah badonbor ki la tur lyngba ïa u paidïapom ki Philistia, bad ki la tong um na kata ka pukri Bethlehem, kaba hajan ka khyrdop, bad ki la shim ïa ka, bad ki la wallam ha u Dabid: hynrei, um treh ban dih ïa ka, hynrei, u la theh noh ha U Trai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u la ong, “Ba ngan leh kum ïa kane, nga em, A Trai: kumno ngan dih ïa ka snam jong kine ki rangbah kiba la kheiñduh ïa la ki mynsiem?” Namar kata keiñ, um treh ban dih ïa ka. Ïa kine kiei kiei ki la leh kita lai ngut ki rangbah badonbor.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Abishai, u para u Joab, u khun ka Seruïah u la long rangbah na kine lai ngut. Te u la rah ïa la u sum pyrshah ïa laispah ngut bad u la pynïap ïa ki, bad u la donnam hapdeng kita lai ngut.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hato um long uba kham donburom na ki lai ngut? namar kata, la pynlong ïa u, u nongïalam jong ki: hynrei, um shym kot haduh ki lai ngut ki banyngkong.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada, u khun jong u rangbah badonbor na Kabsil, uba la leh ïa ki kam ki bakhraw, u la pynïap ïa ki ar ngut ki khun u Ariel na Moab: u la leit hiar ruh bad u la pynïap ïa u sing hapoh ka thliew ha ka por hap ïor.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u la pynïap ïa u nong Ijipt, u rangbah babhabriew: te uta u nong Ijipt u la don u sum ha la ka kti; hynrei, u la leit hiar sha u da u diengduh, bad u la knieh ïa uta u sum na ka kti uta u nong Ijipt, bad u la pynïap ïa u da u sum jong u hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ïa kine kiei kiei u la leh u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada, bad u la donnam hapdeng kita ki lai ngut ki rangbah.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U la kham donburom ban ïa kita ki laiphew ngut, hynrei, um shym kot haduh kita ki lai ngut ki banyngkong. Bad u Dabid u la buh ïa u halor ki nongap phira jong u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U Asahel u para u Joab u la long uwei na kita ki laiphew ngut; u Elhanan u khun u Dodo na Bethlehem;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> u Shammah u nong Harod, u Elika u nong Harod;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> u Heles u nong Palti, u Ira u khun u Ikkesh u nong Tekoa;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> u Abieser u nong Anathoth, u Mebunai u nong Hushath:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> u Salmon u kynja Ahohi, u Maharai u nong Netophath;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> u Heleb u khun u Baanah u nong Netophath, u Ittai u khun u Ribai na Gibeah jong ki khun u Benjamin;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> u Benaïah u nong Pirathon, u Hiddai na ki wah duid ka Gaash;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> u Abi-albon u nong Arbath, u Asmabeth u nong Barhum;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> u Eliahba u nong Shaalbon, ki khun u Jashen, u Jonathan;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> u Shammah u nong Harar, u Ahiam u khun u Sharar u nong Arar;",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> u Eliphelet u khun u Ahasbai, u khun u kynja Maakath, u Eliam u khun u Ahithophel u nong Gilon;",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> u Hesro u nong Karmel, u Paarai u nong Arbit;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> u Igal u khun u Nathan na Sobah, u Bani u nong Gad:",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> u Selek u kynja Ammon, u Naharai u nong Beeroth, ki nongrah atiar jong u Joab u khun ka Seruïah;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> u Ira u nong Ithri, u Gareb u nong Ithri;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> u Uriah u nong Hit: laiphew hynñiew ngut baroh."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ka jingbitar U Trai ka la meh pat ïa ki Israel, bad u la pynkhih ïa u Dabid pyrshah ïa ki, u da ong, “Khie da kheiñ ïa ki Israel bad ïa ki Judah.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u syiem u la ong ha u Joab u kaptan jong u paidïapom, uba la don lem bad u, “Khie leit te kylleng ïa ki jaid Israel baroh, naduh Dan haduh Beer-sheba, bad to kheiñ ïa u paidlang, ba ngan ïoh tip ïa ka jingkheiñ jong u paidlang.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Joab, te u la ong ha u syiem, “To U Trai U Blei jong me un pynroi ïa u paidbah shispah shah la ki long katno katno, bad to ai ba ki khmat u syiem kynrad jong nga kin ïohi ïa kata, hynrei, balei ba u syiem kynrad jong nga u mon kum ïa kane?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Pynban, ka la kham lah ka ktien u syiem ban ïa u Joab, bad ban ïa ki kaptan u paidïapom. Te u Joab bad ki kaptan u paidïapom ki la mih noh na khmat u syiem, ïa ka ban kheiñ ïa u paidbah Israel.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ki la leit sha shiliang ka Jordan, bad ki la shong dara ha Aroer, sha kamon jong kata ka shnong kaba hapdeng ka them Gad, bad haduh Jaser:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> hadien kata, ki la poi sha Gilead, bad sha ka ri Tahtim-hodsi; bad ki la poi sha Dan-jaan, bad sawdong kylleng haduh Sidon,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad ki la poi sha ka kut baskhem ka Tyros, bad sha ki nongbah ki Hib baroh, bad ki jong ki Kanaan: bad ki la leit sha ka phang shathie ka Judah, ha Beer-sheba.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumta, haba ki la leit kylleng ïa ka ri baroh, ki la wan sha Jerusalem ynda la dap khyndai bnai bad arphew sngi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Joab u la ai noh ha u syiem ïa ka jingkheiñ ka jingñiew ïa u paidbah; te ha Israel ki la don phraspah hajar ki rangbah badonbor kiba rah waitlam; bad ki rangbah Judah ki la long sanspah hajar ngut.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ka dohnud u Dabid ka la shoh ïa u, hadien ba u la kheiñ ïa u paidbah. Bad u Dabid u la ong ha U Trai, “Nga la leh pop shikatdei ha kaba nga la leh: hynrei mynta, A Trai, nga kyrpad ïa me, to pyndam noh ïa ka jingleh bymman u shakri jong me; naba nga la leh bieit eh.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te haba u Dabid u la khie mynstep, ka ktien U Trai ka la wan ha u Gad u nongïathuhlypa, u nongïohi u Dabid, da kaba ong,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Khie leit kren ha u Dabid, ‘Kumne u ong U Trai: Nga buh ha me lai tylli kiei kiei; to jied ha me kawei na ki, ba ngan leh ïa kata ha me.’ ”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kumta, u Gad u la wan ha u Dabid, bad u la ïathuh ha u, bad u la ong ha u, “Kan wan ha me hynñiew snem ka 'nemsniew ha ka ri jong me? lane me mon ban phet ïap lai bnai ha khmat ki nongshun jong me haba ki beh ïa me? lane kan long ka jingïapthem lai sngi ha ka ri jong me? mynta to pyrkhat, bad to sngap da kaba kumno ngan phai ktien ha uta uba la phah ïa nga.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Gad, “Nga pisa eh: to ngin ïahap te ha ka kti U Trai: naba ki jingisynei jong u kiba khraw; te wat ai ngan hap ha ka kti u briew.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kumta, U Trai u la phah ka jingïapthem ha Israel naduh kata ka step haduh kata ka por ba la buh: bad ki la ïap na ki paidbah naduh Dan haduh Beer-sheba hynñiewphew hajar ki rangbah.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te haba uta u angel u la kner ïa la ka kti sha Jerusalem ïa ka ban pynjot ïa ka, U Trai u la kylla-ka-bamut shaphang kane ka jingpynsniew, bad u la ong ha uta u angel uba pynjot ïa u paidbah, “Keiñ noh katto; to pynsangeh ïa la ka kti.” Te uta u angel U Trai u la don hajan ka kyntem u Araunah u nong Jebus.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U Dabid te u la kren ha U Trai haba u la ïohi ïa uta u angel uba la shoh ïa u paidbah, bad u la ong, “Ha khmih, nga, nga la leh pop, bad nga, nga la leh kiat: hynrei, kine ki langbrot, ki la leh aïu kine? nga kyrpad ïa me, to ka kti jong me kan long halor jong nga, bad halor ka ïing u kpa jong nga.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Gad u la wan ha u Dabid ha kata ka sngi, bad u la ong ha u, “Khie leit kiew, tei ka duwan ha U Trai ha kata ka kyntem u Araunah u nong Jebus.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u Dabid u la leit kiew katba kum ka ktien u Gad, kumba la hukum U Trai.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U Araunah te u la khmih, bad u la ïohi ïa u syiem bad ki shakri jong u ba ki nang wan sha u: bad u Araunah u la mih noh, bad u la dem ngon la ka khmat ha khmat u syiem.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u Araunah u la ong, “Namar balei ba u syiem kynrad jong nga u la wan ha la u shakri?” Te u Dabid u la ong, “Ïa ka ban thied ïa kane ka kyntem na me, ïa ka ban tei ka duwan ha U Trai, ba un pynsangeh na u paidbah ïa kane ka jingïapthem.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Araunah u la ong ha u Dabid, “To un shim u syiem kynrad jong nga bad un ainguh ïa kaba u ibit: ha khmih, kine ki masi dab ban long ka jingainguh thang, bad kita ki tiar shoh kba, bad ki tiar jong ki masi dab ban long diengïap:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ïa kane baroh, ko syiem, u ai u Araunah ha u syiem.” Bad u Araunah u la ong ha u syiem, “To U Trai U Blei jong me un pdiang sngewbha ïa me.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U syiem te u la ong ha u Araunah, “Em; hynrei, ngan thied hi keiñ ïa ka na me da ka dor: lymne ngan ym ainguh ha U Trai U Blei jong nga da ki jingainguh thang kiba shu ïoh ei.” Kumta, u Dabid u la thied ïa kata ka kyntem bad ïa ki masi dab sanphew ki shekel rupa.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Dabid u la tei ïa ka duwan hangta ha U Trai, bad u la ainguh da ki jingainguh thang bad da ki jingainguh pynïasuk. Kumta U Trai u la ïasuk bad ka ri, bad la pynsangeh ïa kata ka jingïapthem na Israel."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;